Vechiduku Vanobvunza Kuti . . .
Ndinoita Sei Kuti Ushoma Hwangu Hupere ?
UNONETSEKANA here paunova nedzihwa ?
Zvimwe haunetsekani .
Unoziva kuti uchanaya .
Asika zvakadini kana zviratidzo zvedzihwa rako zvikapfuurira ?
Ipapo ungava nechimwe chinhu chakakomba zvikuru chinopfuura dzihwa rinopfuura , uye unoita zvakanaka kuva anoitira hanya .
Kumwe chetekwo ndozvakunoitawo paunova noushoma .
Nhambo zhinjisa dzoushoma ndedzechinguvana .
* Asika dzimwe nguva kurwadza kunotambudza kwoushoma kunopfuurira .
Panoratidzika kuva pasina nzira yokubuda nayo .
Ronny , mudzidziswa wapachikoro chapamusoro , anorondedzera , kuti : “ Ndave ndichienda kuchikoro muruwa rwuno kwamakore masere , asi munguva iyoyi yose handina kutongokwanisa kuita shamwari imwe chete ! . . .
Hapana munhu anoziva chandinorangarira uye hapana munhu anoitira hanya .
Dzimwe nguva ndinofunga kuti handigoni chaizvoizvo kukukurirazve ! ” — Preparing for Adolescence .
SaRonny , vechiduku vazhinji vanotambura inowanzonzi ushoma hunopfuurira .
Zvimwe iwe unonzwa uku kusava nechinhu kunorwadza .
Kana zvakadaro , rega kupererwa nezano rose zvaro .
Chokwadi , ushoma hunopfuurira hahuzati huri chinetso chiduku .
Hwakakomba zvikuru kupfuura ushoma hwechinguvana .
Chokwadika , vanodaro vanzveri , zvivirizvo “ zvakasiana sedzihwawo zvaro nechibayo . ”
Asi chibayowo zvacho chinogona kurapwa , ushoma hunopfuurira hunogona kukurirwawo .
Asika seiko ?
Kunyange kuva noushoma kuri chinhu chapanhambo nenhambo kana kuti nzira inosuruvarisa youpenyu nokuda kwako , nhanho yokutanga mukuwana mushonga ndeyokunzwisisa chisakiso chahwo .
Soromoni Mambo wekare akacherekedza , kuti : “ Munhu wokunzwisisa ndiye uyo anowana nhungamiro younyanzvi . ” — Zvirevo 1 : 5 .
Rhonda wezera ramakore ane gumi namatanhatu anoratidzira chisakiso chikurusa chinozivikanwa noushoma hunopfuurira mukutaura , kuti : “ Ndinofunga kuti chikonzero nei ndichinzwa ndine ushoma zvikuru ndechokuti — chokwadi haugoni kuva neshamwari kana uchirangarira zvakashata pamsoro pako umene .
Uye ndinofunga kuti handizvidi ini ndimene zvikuru kwazvo . ” — Lonely in America .
Ushoma hwaRhonda hunobva mukati .
Kuzvirangarira kwake kwakaderera kunoumba mhinganidzo inomudzivisa kutanga ndokuita shamwari .
Unova nemifungo yake here ?
Anodaro mumwe munzveri : “ Mifungo yakadai seyokuti ‘ Ini handisati ndichiyevedza , ’ ‘ Ini handisati ndichifadza , ’ ‘ Ini handina maturo , ’ misoro inozivikanwa pakati poushoma hunopfuurira . ”
Kuzvirangarira kwakaderera , kunoparirawo kutya kwokuva anorambwa .
Anoyeuka kudaro Steven : “ Ndakanga ndichida kutaura pamsoro pokunzwa kwangu kwoushoma , asika handina kuziva chaizvoizvo mashoko okukutaura nawo .
Ndakanga ndichitya kuti vanhu vaizondiseka kana kuti vaisazondirangarira zvakakomba .
Kwakanga kwakaoma chaizvoizvo kutaura . ”
Nokudaro , vechiduku vamwe vanonyarara , ndokutambura kunyarara .
Ko ikoku kungashandurwa sei ?
Vaka Kuzviremekedza Kwako
Chinhu chikuru chokukurira ushoma chiri mukuvaka kuzviremekedza kwako .
Muapostora Pauro akanyora , kuti : “ Nokuti kupfurikidza netsitsi dzakakomba dzandakapiwa ndinozivisa munhu ari wose ari pakati penyu kusazvifunga zvikuru iye amene kupfuura kufunga kuri madikanwa . ”
Ikoku kunoratidzira kuti mwero wokuzviremekedza uri madikanwa .
Bhaibheri , nokuda kweichi chikonzero , rinonyevera pamsoro pokusanyanyozvifunga zvikuru bedzi asiwo kunyanyozvifunga zviduku kwako umene .
Kunze kwezvo , Jehovha akapa munhu mavara akafanana naaMwari .
Naizvozvo kusvikira kutambanuko yakati kuti iwe una mavara iwawo anoyevedza mauri .
Unozvininipisa , uno mwero , unodzidzisika here ?
Kana kuti une rupo , unonzwira ngoni , uno mutsa here ?
Rega kuzvipofumadzira iwe umene kumavara iwawo .
Zvimwe iwe unogonawo kukudziridza humwe hunyanzvi hunobetsera namavara .
Chokwadi , pangava nezvimwe zvinhu pamsoro pako zvausingadi , somuenzaniso zvitarisiko zvako .
Huzvipirei mhaka iwe umene nokuda kwechimwe chinhu chausingagoni kuchinja ?
Panzvimbo pakwo , shandira mavara asina kunaka aunogona kuchinja , akadai sechinya , hasha dzakashata , kana kuti udyire .
Wana nguva yokukudziridza icho Bhaibheri rinoidza kuti “ hunhu hutsva , ” hunoratidzirwa nomutsa , kuzvininipisa kwendangariro , nounyoro .
Kuzviremekedza kwako umene kuchawedzera !
Kupfuurirazve , zvaunodzidza kuzvida iwe umene , vamwe vachakweverwa kumavara ako anofadza .
Asika sezvaunogona kuona bedzi mavara azere eruva pashure pokunge rabumbunuka , naizvozvo vamwe vanogona bedzi kuona zvizere mavara ako kana ukataura kwavari .
‘ Asika ndinogona sei kuita izvozvo ? ’
ungabvunza kudaro .
“ Pamhamha ” Kusvikira Kuna Vamwe
‘ Zano rakanakisisa nokuda kwomunhu ane ushoma , ’ chinodaro chinyorwa chazvino uno chokuU.S .
National Institute of Mental Health , ndero‘kubatanidzwa navamwe vanhu . ’
Iri zano rinotsinhirana nezano reBhaibheri roku “ pamhamha ” ndokuratidzira “ kunzwirana urombo , ” kana kuti kunzwa kwokuzvipinza munzvimbo yomumwe .
Kunoshanda .
Imwe fundo , yakabudiswa mumagazini yeAdolescence , inoratidzira kuti ‘ vechiduku vanoratidzira kuitira hanya mugarikano yavamwe havazati vane ushoma savechiduku vasingaitiri hanya . ’
Neiko ?
Kutarisira vamwe hakuzati kuchingoita kuti ndangariro yako ibve paushoma hwako bedzi asi kunokuchidzira vamwe kufarira mauri .
Vanhu vachawanzodavidza kupfurikidza nokukuitirawo mutsa .
Ko zvino , unogona sei kutanga ?
Kutanga Kutaura
Natalie wezera ramakore gumi namapfumbamwe akasarudza kuti iye aizoita zvakawanda zvinopfuura kunyarara ndokumirira vanhu kutanga kuti mhoro .
‘ Ndinotofanira kuva ane ushamwariwo , ’ iye anodaro .
‘ Neimwe nzira vanhu vachafunga kuti ndakanyarara . ’
Naizvozvo tanga nokunyemwerera .
Mumwe munhu anganyemwererawo .
Nhanho inotevera , kutanga kurukurirano kwakaoma zvikuru .
Lillian , wezera ramakore 15 , anobvuma , kuti : “ Kusvika vaeni kwenguva yokutanga kwakanga kuchityisa zvomenemene .
Ndakanga ndichitya kuti ivo havasati vaizondigamuchira . ”
Ko Lillian anotanga sei kurukurirano ?
“ Ndinobvunza mibvunzo yakapfava , ” iye anodaro , “ yakadai sokuti , ‘ Munobva kupiko ? ’
‘ Munoziva nyakuti here ? ’
Isu tose tiri vaviri tingave tichiziva mumwe munhu , uye isati iri nguva refu tave kutaura . ”
Zvinoitika zvinogoveranwa zvinogonawo kubatira sezvokutanga kutaura .
Anne wezera ramakore gumi namasere anowedzera , kuti : “ Handisati ndichitanga nokutaura pamsoro pechimwe chinhu chapedyo pedyo nokuti mumwe munhu anovhiringidzwa kana kuti kutyiswa uye achandidzivisa . ”
Hungu , hakuzati kuri kuchenjera kupinda mukurukurirano yakadzama pakarepo .
Kunyange zvazvo zvakadaro , zvakadiniko kana padzimwe nguva usingatongozivi hako chokutaura ?
Eya , panogarova nezvinhu zvaunogona kuita .
Bhaibheri rinotiudza nezvomukadzi ainzi Dhorkasi wai “ shingaira zvikuru pamabasa akanaka ezvipo ” nokuda kwechirikadzi dzinoshaiwa .
Paakafa , chirikadzi dzakachema nokuda kworusuruvaro .
Zviito zvaDhorkasi zvomutsa zvakanga zvamuita kuti adiwe nadzo .
Mabasa omutsa nomudzimu worupo nenzira yakafanana zvichakubetsera kuvaka ushamwari hunokosha .
Asika iva wechokwadi .
Dzidza kubvuma kuti vamwe vanhu havasati vachizodavidza kunyemwerero yako namhoro woushamwari .
Kana zvakadaro , ivo vane chinetso — kwete iwe .
Kugadzikisa Migariro Yakashata
Zvakare , vechiduku vazhinji vanotambura ushoma padzimwe nguva .
Yeuka kuti kungava kwechinguvana uye kuchiparirwa nemigariro yausingagoni kudzora .
Kupfuura kwenguva kuchawanzokubetsera kugadzikisa migariro yakashata .
Ushoma huchapfuura .
Ushoma hunopfuurira , zvisinei hazvo , hunobva mukati uye hunogona kuparirwa nokuzvirangarira kwakaderera .
Kana zvakadaro , ita chiito !
‘ Shandura ndangariro yako ’ uye ‘ pfeka hunhu hutsva , ’ rinodaro Shoko raMwari .
Hungu , vaka kuzviremekedza kwako umene kupfurikidza nokukudziridza mavara anofadza aunawo mauri .
Ita zvinhu nokuda kwavamwe vanhu , uye ivo vachawanzodavidza kwauri .
Zvisinei , pasinei zvapo nokuti vanhu vanoita sei , unogona kuva neshamwari isingatongokurambi .
Ndianiko iyeyo ?
Jesu Kristu akaudza vadzidzi vake , kuti : “ Imi muchandisiya ndiri ndoga ; asi ini handisati ndiri ndoga bedzi , nokuti Baba vaneni . ”
Uhu hushamwaridzani chaihwoihwo naJehovha hwakasimbaradza Jesu mukati menhambo dzokuva oga .
Jehovha anogona kuvawo shamwari yako chaiyoiyo zvikuru .
Ziva hunhu hwake kupfurikidza nokurava Bhaibheri nokucherekedza chisiko chake .
Simbaradza ushamwari hwako naye kupfurikidza nomunyengetero .
Nokukurumidza uchawana kuti ushamwaridzani naJehovha Mwari ndiyo mhinduro yakaisvonakisisa youshoma hwako .
[ Mashoko Omuzasi ]
