Vechiduku Vanobvunza Kuti . . . Ndinogona Sei Kutarisira Mari Yangu ?
UNORANGARIRA sei pamusoro pemari ?
Ndichimwe chinhu chokupambadza nenzira yaunoda here ?
Ndichimwe chinhu chinoda kuchengetwa kunyange kutarisirwa here ?
Nomutoo wakajeka , dzichiziva kuti vabereki vadzo varipo kuti vadzigovere , pwere zhinji , hadzirangariri pamusoro pemari — kunze kwokuti dzingaishandisa sei .
Hunyanguvezvo , nguva dzose ungave usati una vabereki vangabatira sekotsekano .
Kupfuurirazve , idiwo zvaro rokuti iwe une basa rapashure pechikoro kana kuti kunyange mvumiro yakati kuti harizati richireva kuti iwe unogona kutsunga kuva asingangwariri nemari .
Bhaibheri rinonyevera , kuti : “ Wakaita kuti meso ako aironge [ mari ] , apo isati iri chinhu here ?
Nokuti pasina kukundikana iyo inozviitira imene mapapiro akaita seawo egondo ndokubhururukira kumatenga . ” Ungagona sei kudzivisa mari yako pa‘kubhururuka ’ ?
Kutanga , iwe unofanira kunzwisisa zviri zvinobatanidzwa nemari . Mari — Chikonzero Nei Ichikosha Kudaro
Mari mutoo wokutsinhana nawo — uye mutoo une simba pana ikoko .
Encyclopædia Britannica rinoreva kuti “ mari ndiyo chinhu bedzi bedzi chaunogona kutenga nacho chinhu chipi nechipi . ”
Somuenzaniso , nhepfenyuro yako ingarangarirwa somudziyo ( chimwe chinhu chinokosha ) .
Asika fungidzira hako uchiedza kuitsinhanisa kana kuti kuishambadza nokuda kwechingwa zvacho .
Nhepfenyuro ingava inopfuura zvikurukuru ukoshi hwechingwa . Asi kana muzvinashopu yebhekari asingadi nhepfenyuro yako , iye sezvinopanikirika angasakupa chingwa nokuda kwayo .
Nhepfenyuro yako ingavawo bedzi isingabetseri !
Mari , kunyange zvazvo zvakadaro , inoremekedzwa munyika yose .
* Nokudaro inokurumidza uye nyore nyore kutsinhaniswa nokuda kwezvinhu zvipi kana zvipi kana kuti mabasa aunoda .
Nomutoo wokuchenjera , ipapoka , Soromoni akataura pana Muparidzi 7 : 12 kuti “ mariwo chitaviridzo . ”
Nokudaro mari chinhu chikurusa chokuva nezvinhu zviri madikanwa uyewo mifaro mizhinji youpenyu .
Sokupfuurira kutaura kwakaita Soromoni , kuti : “ Tafura rine mufaro waro , uye waini inoita upenyu hunofadza ; uye mari ndiyo chisakiso chakwo kwose . ” — Muparidzi 10 : 19 , The New English Bible .
Asika , mari haizati ichiwanzowanwa nyore nyore .
Vabereki vazhinjisa havazati vane manyuko asina kuganhurirwa emari ; vanofanira kushanda nesimba nokuda kwezvavanogoverana newe .
Soromoni akabvunza , kuti : “ Ko munhu anosvika pakuva nechii nokuda kwebasa rake rose resimba ? ”
Vabereki vako vangagutsikana zvishoma — uye muripo muduku — nokuda kwebasa ravo resimba .
Chokwadika , vabereki vanoshanda kubvira mangwanani kusvikira usiku kuti vagovere bedzi mhuri dzavo nezviri madikanwa zvoupenyu !
Mari , ipapoka , haisati ichifanira kurerutswa .
Inofanira kurangarirwa noruremekedzo ndokutarisirwa nomutoo wokuchenjera .
Nzira imwe yokuita nayo ikoku ndeyokudzidza kuronga mari yako inoshandiswa .
Ukoshi Hwokuronga Mari Inoshandiswa
Kuronga mari inoshandiswa kunongova bedzi mutoo wokutarisira nawo kushandiswa nokuchengetwa kwemari yako .
Magazini ye’Teen yaMay 1985 yakati : “ Kuwana uko madhora ako ose ari ‘ kunyangarikira ’ ndiyo nhano yokutanga yokuwana udzori pamari yako ndokuzviisa iwe umene pakurongwa kwemari inoshandiswa iyo ichakubetsera . ”
Naizvozvo kutanga ita rudungwe rwendyiko dzako dzose dzinokarirwa — mari yezvokudya zvamasikati , mari yezvokufambisa , mari yevaraidzo , zvichingunodaro .
Tevere , ramba uchinzvera ndyiko dzako chaidzoidzo nokuda kwomwedzi kana kuti inopfuura .
Zvino wokwanisa kuita nharidzano dzino mufungo uye chaidzoidzo dzokushandisa mari nokuchengeta .
Kana izvozvi zvangotangwa bedzi , ungaedza kutora emvuropu dzakati kuti ndokudzinyora mukuwirirana neboka rimwe nerimwe rendyiko .
Emvuropu imwe , somuenzaniso , inganyorwa kuti “ Mari Yezvokudya , ” nepo imwe inganyorwa nokuda kwokutenga kumwe kwomunguva yemberi , kwakadai se “ Bhurauzi Idzva ” kana kuti “ Hembe Itsva . ”
Paunogamuchira mvumiro yako kana kuti muripo , kamuranisira mari mumaemvuropu mukuwirirana nenharidzano dzako dzakagadzwa .
Apo ndyiko dzinobuda , dziripire kubva mumaemvuropu akakodzera . *
Wati wamboedza kutevera kurongwa kwemari inoshandiswa ndokukundikana here ?
Hauzati uri woga bedzi . Leah , imwe mhandara , yakati : “ Ndakaedza kuronga mari yangu inoshandiswa pachiverengero chakati kuti chenhambo , asi handigoni kusanoomerera kukurongwa kwemari yangu . ”
Zvisinei , iye anobvuma , kuti : “ Apo ndinoronga mari yangu inoshandiswa , ndinochengeta mari zviri nani zvikuru .
Handizati ndichitenga zvinhu zvandisingashaiwi . ”
Chii chiri chinhu chikuru chorubudiriro ?
Kuzviranga . Ita chisarudzo ndokuomerera kwachiri ! Inzwa wakasunungukawo , kunyengetera kuna Jehovha kukubetsera kudzora miitiro ipi neipi yokusazvidzora yokushandisa mari . — Ruka 11 : 13 .
Nomutoo unofadza , muapostora Pauro akakarakadza kuti maKristu omuKorinte “ aronge ” imwe yemari yawo , achiti : “ Zuva riri rose rokutanga revhiki mumwe nomumwe wenyu paimba yake amene ngaatsaure chimwe chinhu achengete . ”
Mariyo ipapo yaizopirwa kumari chaidzo nokuda kwamaKristu anoshaiwa .
Mukusapanikira kwaida kuzviranga chaikoiko kuti maKristu iwawo eKorinte atevere chikarakadzo chomuapostora Pauro , asi zvikomborero zvakaita kuti nhamburiko yakadaro ive yakakukodzera !
Iwewo pasina panikiro unobetserekana nokuomerera pakurongwa kwemari .
Imwe pwere inonzi Avian inoti : “ Ini ndakanga ndakaita somunhu anodudzwa pana Zvirevo 21 : 5 , “ unokurumidzisa ” uye ‘ unogovangira kushaiwa ’ pamberi pezuva rinotevera rokutambira .
Kuronga mari kunondiita ndive ane mutoro zvikuru . ”
Ngwarira Nezvikwereti “ Tenga zvino ungoripira gare gare ! ”
vanokurudzira kudaro vatengesi vazhinji .
Chichishandiswa nomutoo wokungwarira uye nomutoo wokuchenjerera , chikwereti zvamazvikwazvo chine nzvimbo yacho .
Zvisinei , chichishandiswa nomutoo wokusangwarira chikwereti chinogona kuva izvo imwe pwere inonzi Kevin yakaidza kuti “ chimiro chouranda . ” — Enzanisira naZvirevo 22 : 7 .
Nokuda kwedzimwe pwere , chikwereti chinongokuita kuve nyore kutenga zvinhu zvadzisingashaiwi kana kuti zvadzisingagoni kutsunga kutenga .
Uye kana usingapedzi kuripira mari yako yasara pakupera kwomwedzi , iwe unochanjwa mhindu pane zvaune ngava nazvo .
Kana ukatora nguva refu kuripira , chinhucho chinoguma nokuchanja mari yakawanda .
Naizvozvo , pakupedzisira , kwakachipa kuchengeta mari yako nokuda kwechaunoshaiwa ndokuchiripira nemari . ‘ Mari Inochengetwa . . . ’
Imwe mhandara inonzi Phyllis yakati : “ Hatizati tichitongoziva apo zvitambudzo zvino uya patiri uye tichadikanirwa kuva nemari yakachengetwa . ”
( Enzanisira Muparidzi 9 : 11 . )
Zvamazvirokwazvo , unogona kurwara ndokusakwanisa kuva nebasa .
Vabereki vakowo vangawirwa nenguva dzinotambudza ndokuva vasingakwanisi kukupa mari yawakabvumirwa .
Naizvozvo kunoita mufungo wakanaka kubatanidza mukuronga mari kwako chitsama chakati kuti chinotsaurwa chemari inochengetwa .
Ikoku kunogona kukubetsera kudzivisa chinetso chemari nomutoo uri nyore zvikuru .
Zvino gaba kana kuti kabhokisi kangaratidzika kuva nzvimbo yakanaka yokuchengetera mari yako .
Jesu , kunyange zvazvo zvakadaro , akataura nezvokuisa mari mubhengi umo inogona kuwana mhindu ndokuwedzera .
Ipapoka , huregererei kukurukura navabereki vako faniro yokuvhura bhuku rako umene reakaundi kubhengi ?
Haudikanirwi hako kuva nechitsama chikuru chemari kuti uite kuti gadziriro yokuchengeta mari kubhengi ishande , kunyange zvazvo kune dzimwe nzvimbo chitsama chakaringanira chichidikanwa kudzivisa kuchanjwa kwebasa .
Chinhu chikurusa chorubudiriro ndechokuva wenguva dzose mukubhanga mari yako .
Zvakadiniko , kunyange zvazvo zvakadaro , kana mhuri yako isine chinhu kana kuti ichigara munyika isine chimuko mune zvemari umo pwere dzisingagarova nemari yadzo dzimene inoshandiswa ?
Hunyanguvezvo , mhuri yako ine zvimwewo zvinhu , kunyange zvazvo zvingava zvishoma .
Asi kana chimiro chako chendangariro kupfuma yemhuri chiri chokuti sezvo ‘ uchiiwana nyore nyore , uchaipambadza nyore nyore , ’ ungarwisana nefariro dzako umene uye nedzemhuri .
Zvamazvirokwazvo , iwe hausati waizoda kubvumikisa kuva “ asingaongi ” pakureva nezvezvinhu vabereki vako vanoshanda nesimba kuti vagovere . — Zvirevo 29 : 21 .
Naizvozvo ratidzira chimiro chendangariro chokuva nomutoro kumari — kunyange kana une mari shomanene kana kuti usina yako umene .
Somuenzaniso , iwe unogona kudzivisa kupambadza zvinhu , zvakadai sezvinhu zvokudya . ( Ona Johane 6 : 12 , 13 . )
Bata zvinhu zvakaoma kutsiva nezvinodya mari yakawanda , zvakadai samagirazi okuona nawo nemigove yechikoro , noruremekedzo .
Pasina panikiro vabereki vako vachaonga zvikurukuru ngwariro yako muna ikoku . Zvirevo 11 : 28 inotiyeuchidza , kuti : “ Unovimba nepfuma yake , uchawa ; asi vakarurama vachanaka seshizha nyoro . ”
Mari inofanira kubatira kutarisira zvinoshaikwa zvedu . Asi muKristu haazati achifanira kubatikana nokuwana pfuma .
Sokutaura kunoita imwe pwere inonzi Matthew , kuti : “ Mari ine nzvimbo yayo , asi iyo haizati iri chinhu chose . ”
Inongova bedzi mudziyo , zvamazvirokwazvo , “ chitaviridzo . ”
Dzidza kushandisa mari nomutoo wokuchenjeri , wokungwara .
Nyaya inotevera ichatsanangura mutoo wokushandisa nawo mari yako nomutoo wokuchenjera kutarisira misengwa yako umene neyemhuri .
[ Mashoko Omuzasi ] Musiano mumwe kuna ikoku waizova munyika umo kuderera kwoukoshi hwemari kwakaita kuti mari inoshandisika yamarudzi ive isitongorina maturo .
