Chikamu 24 : Zvino nokusingaperi — Runako Rusingagumi Rworudzidziso Rwechokwadi
“ Rudzidziso , kana rwakapfeka zvokwadi dzokudenga , runodikanirwa kuonwa kuti rugoyemurwa . ” — Willam Cowper , munyori wenhetembo weEngland womuzana ramakore rechi 18
