Kuziva Rudzidziso Rwako Sorwechokwadi Kana Kuti Rwenhema
▪ Rudzidziso rwechokwadi runokuchidzira muvanamati varwo chisungo chisingadambuki chorudo nechinzwano chisati chichitapurwa nemiganhu yourudzi .
Rudzidziso rwenhema harukuchidziri rudo rwakadaro .
Panzvimbo pezvo , mukutevedzera Kaini , mitezo yarwo inoenda ndokuurayana muhondo dzamarudzi ose . — 1 Johane 3 : 10 - 12 .
▪ Rudzidziso rwechokwadi runoramba rusitongorina zvamatongerwe enyika zvavanhu uye runotarira kuMusiki kuti apedze zvinetso zvenyika kupfurikidza nehurumende yake yoUmambo .
Rudzidziso rwenhema runotevera muenzaniso waNimirodhi paShongwe yeBhabheri .
Runozvibatanidza rumene nezvamatongerwe enyika , runovimba navanamwari vezvamatongerwe enyika vane nhau dzarwunopindira , uye nokudaro runovanzarika hwaro nokuda kworuparadziko rwarwo rumene . — Dhanieri 2 : 44 ; Johane 18 : 36 ; Jakobho 1 : 27 .
▪ Rudzidziso rwechokwadi runoziva Jehovha saMwari wechokwadi , uyo bedzi anokwanisa kununura mudzvinyiriro .
