Rudzidziso rwenhema — somuenzaniso , chiBuddha — chinorangarira upenyu pasi pano kuva chimwe chinhu chisingashuviwi uye sechimwe chinhu chokusunungurwa pachiri munguva yemberi isina chokwadi . — Pisarema 37 : 29 ; Zvakazarurwa 21 : 3 , 4 .
▪ Rudzidziso rwechokwadi , kupfurikidza nebhuku raro dzvene , Bhaibheri , runozadza vanhu nokutenda kusingazununguki ; runovapa tariro ine chipikirwa uye runovakuchidzirira kumabasa erudo rwechokwadi kuna Mwari nomuvakidzani .
Rudzidziso rwenhema , pasinei hapo namabhuku aro matsvene , zvikurukuru harubudiriri mukuita zvinhu izvozvo . — 1 Johane 5 : 3 , 4 .
▪ Rudzidziso rwechokwadi runoratidzirwa navatariri vanozvininipisa .
Rudzidziso rwenhema runocherekedzwa navatungamiriri varwo vane gwinyiro , navane ndangariro yokuzvimirira , avo vanodisa kumonyanisa zvokwadi uye vanotsvaka mhindu yezvamatongerwe enyika kana kuti yenyika . — Mabasa 20 : 28 , 29 ; 1 Petro 5 : 2 , 3 .
▪ Rudzidziso rwechokwadi , nzira yakafanira yokuzviisa pasi paMwari , runoshandisa munondo womudzimu , kwete chaiwoiwo .
Rudzidziso rwenhema , pane rumwe rutivi , runobvumiranisa pane zvisina kufanira dzidziso yechokwadi , runoputsa kusatora rutivi kwechiKristu , uye runoronda itiro hanya dzavanhu kupfuura fariro dzoumwari . — 2 VaKorinte 10 : 3 - 5 .
