Kuno rumwe rutivi , mbuya , namakore avo oruzivo rwokuzviwanira mukurovedzwa kwavana , nomutoo womuzvarirwo vanonzwa kuti ivo ndivo vanokwaniriswa kupa pangiro .
Zvisinei , pangiro iyeyo inowanzorangarirwa setsoropodzo , uye kakavadzano inomuka .
Takako aitofanira kubata neichi chinetso apo iye airanga mwanakomana wake muduku .
Amai vomurume wake uye mbuya vakamhanyira mukamuri rake kundomudzivisa , vachidanidzira kunyange nenzwi guru zvikuru kupinda mwana ari kuchema .
Achinzwa atyisidzirwa , Takako akarega kuranga mwanakomana wake .
Gare gare , achiziva ukoshi hwokugovera rovedzo , akasarudza kutangazve rovedzo yakadaro . — Zvirevo 23 : 13 ; VaHebheru 12 : 11 .
Vamwe amai vanogara muYokohama vaikakavadzanawo navamwene vavo pashure pokunge vana vaberekwa .
Amai vaishatirirwa kuti mbuya vaipa vana zvokudyira - dyira pakati pezvokudya zvokuti ivo vaitova vatonyanyoguta zvokusagona kudya zvokudya zvavo .
Achitsinhira pamusoro peichi chinetso , Dr .
Saito anoti : “ [ Vanambuya ] vanopa zviwitsi nemvumiro kuvazukuru vavo .
Vanonyanyisa kugutsa zvishuvo zvoudyire zvepwere .
Munguva pfupi , vanoshatsa vazukuru nokusingaperi . ”
Iye anopangira kuti vanamai vaduku vajekese kuti havasati vachizobvumira pamusoro perovedzo yavana .
Kupitsirana Nokuda Kwechidakadaka
Mune iyi kakavadzano pakati pavamwene nomuroora , pane chimwe chinhu chokusava nomufungo zvikuru chinobate basa .
“ Kutaura mumufungo , ” anotsanangura kudaro Dr .
Saito , “ amai vanorangarira kuti muroora akavabvutira mwanakomana wavo .
Chokwadi , ivo havazati vachitaura chaizvo mufungo wakadaro , sezvo ikoku kuri kwohuhwana zvikurusa .
Asi , nechomukati , mufungo wokuva vakabirwa chidakadaka chomwanakomana wavo wakasimba zvikurukuru mavari . ”
Muuyo ndiwo ukama hunotambura , kana asati ari mapitse chaiwoiwo pakati pohuviri hwavo .
Iyi kombamiro inoratidzika kuva inokudziridzika sezvo mwero wemhuri unoderera .
Navana vashomanene zvikuru vokutarisira , amai vanonzwa vari pedyo zvikuru nomwanakomana wavo .
Pashure pamakore mazhinji okugara nomwanakomana wavo , vanosanoziva zvaanoda nezvaasingadi .
Kunyange zvazvo mwenga mutsva achishuva kufadza murume wake , anoshaiwa iyi zivo chaiyoiyo , zvimwe pakutanga .
Mudzimu wamakwikwi nokudaro ungasatana kukudziridzika , vamwene nomuroora vachipitsirana nokuda kwezvidakadaka zvomurume mumwe cheteyo .
Chinjo Yengwavaira
Mumazuva ekare muJapan pasi pouzivi hwaConfucius , apo kakavadzano dzakadaro dzomumhuri dzaiitika , muroora aidzoserwa — aichatanurwa .
Uye iwowu ndiwo waiva mugumo wenhau yacho .
Zvisinei , nhasi mugariro wacho wasiana .
Chifo cheHondo yeNyika II , chizvarwa chiduku chakatora udzori hwechikwama chemhuri , uye chizvarwa chekare chiri kurasikirwa nepesvedzero yacho nechiremera .
Pashoma napashoma , mugariro wacho wakachinja .
Zvino vabereki vakwegura vari kusiiwa muzvipatara nomumasangano anochengeta vakweguru .
Haiwa kunosuruvarisa sei kuona uyu mugariro munzanga umo ruremekedzo nokuda kwavakweguru rwaichimbova muitiro !
Kombamiro yokurasha vakweguru inogona kuchinjwa sei ?
