Bvumirano ine mufungo inofanira kusvikwa pamusoro pokuti ndiani anofanira kuita zvisarudzo
Kufarikanya Ukama Hwoushamwari Hwehama Dzomuroorano
FUJIKO , muroora ane shungu adudzwa munyaya yokutanga , pakupesvedzera murume wake kutama muimba yababa vake ndokupinda muimba imwe yavakavakidzana nayo .
Asi zvinhu hazvina kuvandudzika zvikuru .
Vhiringidzo inoitwa nehama dzomuroorano dzake yakapfuurira uye kupererwa nezano kwake kwakapfuurira .
Ipapo pane rimwe zuva muenzi akamushanyira .
Shanyo iyeyo yakatanga Fujiko kuchinja panzira yakaguma nohunhu hwakachinja , uye iyoyi yakavandudza ukama hwake navamwe .
Akavamba kufunda Bhaibheri neZvapupu zvaJehovha .
Mukufambira mberi kwenguva , chimiro chake chendangariro chakachinja zvikuru kwazvo zvokuti sezawani wake vakada kupinda fundodzo kuti vazvionere ivo vamene kuti ‘ rwakanga rwuri rudzii rworudzidziso rwakanga rwachinja zvikuru hunhu hwake . ’
Kuziva Chisungo Chitsva
Bhaibheri rinopa mufananidzo wakajeka wegadziriro yapaMagwaro yeroorano .
Pashure pokunge Mwari asika vaviri vokutanga vohunhu ndokuvaisa pamwe chete , iye akagadza nheyo inotevera : “ Murume achasiya baba vake naamai vake uye iye achanamatira kumudzimai wake uye ivo vanofanira kuva nyama imwe . ”
Naizvozvo vanyakuroorana vatsva vanofanira kuziva kuti ivo vapinda muchisungo chitsva .
Vanofanira zvino kunamatirana semhuri inozvimirira kunyange zvazvo ivo vangave vachigara nehama dzavo dzomuroorano .
Zvisinei , kusiya baba naamai hakuzati kuchireva kuti vana apo ivo vanoroora vanogona kutendeutsira makotsi avo pana vabereki vavo uye kuti ivo havazati vachadazve kuvaremekedza nokuvakudza .
“ Usazvidza amai vako nemhaka bedzi yokuti ivo vachembera , ” rinoraira kudaro Bhaibheri .
Asika , neroorano , pane gadziridzo muukama .
Chero bedzi mutezo mumwe nomumwe wemhuri uchisanorangarira iyoyi , vanyakuroorana vechiduku vanogona kubetserekana noruzivo rwokuzviwanira nouchenjeri hwavabereki .
Timotio , jaya rine mukurumbira wakanaka iro muapostora Pauro akaenda naro panzendo dzake dzoushumiri , akarerwa naamai vake vechiJudha , Juniki .
Zvisinei , ambuya vake Roisi sezvinooneka vakavawo nebetsero kuumba upenyu hwake .
Ikoku hakuzati kuri kureva kuti vanambuya vane maruramiro okupindira mukurovedzwa kwavana ndokugadza mipimo yakasiana neyeyo yavabereki .
Pane mutoo wakakodzera umo chizvarwa chekare chinogona kubetsera vechiduku mukurovedzwa kwavana . — Tito 2 : 3 - 5 .
“ Mukadzi Wakachenjera Zvamazvirokwazvo ”
Kana zvizvarwa zviviri zvichizobatira pamwe munhau yakakomba yakadai sokurovedza vana , vose vari vaviri vanofanira kuita muuchenjeri .
“ Mukadzi akachenjera zvamazvirokwazvo akavaka imba yake , ” chinodaro chirevo cheBhaibheri , “ asi benzi rinoikoromora namaoko aro rimene . ”
Ko mukadzi anogona sei kuvaka imba yake ?
Tomiko anotaura kuti yakanga iri kurukurirano yakamubetsera kubatanidza ukama hwake nomuroora wake , Fujiko .
“ Uko kusina kurukurirano yapachivande kune kukangaidzika kwerongedzero , ” rinozanura kudaro Bhaibheri . — Zvirevo 15 : 22 .
Kurukurirano haizati ichireva kutaura kwokusachenjera chinhu chiri chose chiri mundangariro mako pasina rangariro nokuda kwokunzwa kwavamwe .
Hepano panoshanda uchenjeri .
“ Munhu akachenjera achateerera ” izvo vamwe vanotaura .
Padzimwe nguva hama dzako dzomuroorano dzingava nechimwe chinhu chokutaura , asi dzichizengurira kutaura idzo dzimene .
Cherekedza , uye ‘ budisa mifungo yadzo . ’
Ipapo ‘ fungisisa ’ usati wataura . — Zvirevo 1 : 5 ; 15 : 28 ; 20 : 5 .
Kuziva nguva yokutaura kunokosha zvikuru .
“ Shoko rinotaurwa panguva yakarurama nokuda kwaro rakafanana namaapuro endarama ari mundiro yesirvheri , ” chinodaro chirevo cheBhaibheri .
Tokiko nomuroora wake vanotaura kuti vanomirira kutosvikira panguva yakarurama vasati vataura mifungo ingatsautsira mumwe munzira isino kururama .
“ Ndinoedza kufunga ndisati ndataura apo ndinoda kuratidzira chimwe chinhu kumuroora wangu , ” anodaro Tokiko .
“ Ndinochengeta mapfundo acho mundangariro mangu ndokutaura apo iye anenge ari muchimiro chendangariro chakanaka uye asina nzara .
Unoonaka , kuri nyore kutsamwiswa apo unenge une nzara . ”
Mukadzi akachenjera acharega kutaura zvakashata nezvehama dzake dzomuroorano .
“ Kunyange tiri vana amwene kana kuti varoora , tinofanira kuva vanoziva kuti zvakashata zvipi nezvipi zvatinotaura nezvomumwe munhu , pakupedzisira zvichava zvinozivikanwa kwavari , ” anodaro Sumie Tanaka , munyori weJapan uyo akagara navamwene vake kwamakore 30 .
Kupfuurezvo , iye anoreverera kusanotaura zvakanaka nezvehama dzomuroorano nomutoo wakananga uye nomutoo usakananga .
Zvakadiniko , kana hama dzako dzomuroorano dzisingadavidzi kunhamburiko dzako ?
Iva Anokanganwira
Zvinetso zvakakomba pakati pehama dzomuroorano zvinowanzoparirwa nezvinhu zvisati zvaizoparira chinetso kudai zvaizoitwa kana kuti zvaizotaurwa nomumwe munhuwo zvake .
Sezvo isu tose tisina kukwana uye “ tichigumburwa mushoko , ” padzimwe nguva tinga‘taura nokusava nomufungo senokubaya kwomunondo . ’
Asika , kuchenjera kusatsamwiswa neshoko riri rose rokusava nomufungo .
Avo vakakurira zvinetso zvehama dzomuroorano vakatetekera zano reBhaibheri , rinoti : “ Pfuurirai kuregererana nokukanganwirana norusununguko kana mumwe munhu ane chisakiso chokugurukutira mumwe . ”
Chokwadi , kungava kusi nyore kuregerera hama dzako dzomuroorano ndokuvakanganwira , zvikurukuru apo pane chisakiso chokugurukuta .
Asi chikonzero chakasimba chokuita kudaro isimbisiro yokuti kupfurikidza nakwo tichawana kanganwiro inobva kuna Mwari iye amene nokuda kwemhosho dzedu . — Mateo 6 : 14 , 15 .
Kunyange munyika dzokuMabvazuva , uko mugamuchidzanwa vanhu vanotevera chiBuddha , chiTao , chiConfucius , uye chiShinto , kuna vazhinji vakafunda Bhaibheri uye vakasvika pakunzwisisa zvokwadi pamusoro poMusiki ane tsitsi .
Nzwisiso yakadaro yakavabetsera kukurira kunoratidzika kuva kunzwa kweshungu kusingadzoreki .
“ Rudo Harutongokundikani ”
Ukama hunofadza hwehama dzomuroorano hunoda nheyo yechokwadi .
Kubetsera hama yomuroorano yakwegura kana kuti inorwara nokuda kwepfungwa yomusengwa hakuzati kuchibetsera nokuda kwoukama hwakanakisisa .
Haruko akaziva ikoko apo vamwene vake vakanga vachifa negomarara .
Aipedza nguva yakawanda yezuva rake ari kuchipatara achitarisira vamwene vake , uye mukuwedzera , aitarisira mhuri yake amene .
Akanga ari muchinetso chakakura zvikuru zvokuti iye pakupedzisira akarashikirwa nevhudzi rake zhinjisa .
Rimwe zuva achicheka nzara dzavamwene vake , iye nomutoo usati uri wamaune akavacheka .
“ Hauzati uchinditarisira zvomenemene ! ” vakataura kudaro vamwene .
Akatyamadzwa namashoko iwawo okusaonga , Haruko haati aigona kudzivisa misodzi yake .
Ipapo iye akaziva kuti mashokowo akuvadza zvikuru kwazvo nokuti iye akanga achiitira chinhu chiri chose vamwene vake nepfungwa yomusengwa .
Iye akasarudza kurega simba rinosunda nokuda kwebasa rake richiva riri rorudo .
Ikoku kwakamugonesa kukurira shungu dzake uye kwakaguma noukama hwakadzorerwa kuna vamwene vake kutozosvikira ivo vafa .
Zvamazvirokwazvo , rudo runorondedzerwa muBhaibheri ndiro chinhu chikuru chokunyaradza kusawirirana kwemhuri .
Rava izvo muapostora Pauro akataura pamusoro pazvo , ndokuona kana usati uchibvumirana nazvo .
“ Rudo rune mwoyo murefu uye rune mutsa , ” akanyora kudaro .
“ Rudo harune godo , haruzvikudzi , haruzvitutumadzi , haruzati ruchiita nomutoo usina kufanira , haruzati ruchizvitsvakira fariro dzarwo rumene , harutsamwiswi . Harurangariri zvakashata .
Harufariri zvisino kururama , asi runofarira zvokwadi .
Runotsungirira zvinhu zvose , runodavira zvinhu zvose , runokarira zvinhu zvose , runotsungirira zvinhu zvose . ”
Hakuzatiwo kuchishamisa kuti Pauro anowedzera , kuti : “ Rudo harutongokundikani . ”
Unogona sei kukudziridza rudo rwakadaro ?
Bhaibheri rinoronga “ rudo ” sorutivi rwe “ chibereko ” chomudzimu waMwari .
Nokudaro , mukuwedzera kunhamburiko dzako umene , kuri madikanwa kuva nomudzimu waMwari kana uchizokudziridza urwu rudzi rworudo .
Kupfuurirazve , unogona kukumbira Jehovha , Mwari weBhaibheri , kukubetsera kuwedzera rudo rwakafanana norwake kuhunhu hwako .
Chokwadika , ikoku kose kunoda kuti udzidze pamusoro pake kupfurikidza nokufunda Shoko rake , Bhaibheri .
Zvapupu zvaJehovha zvichava zvinofara zvikurusa kukubetsera , sezvazvakaita Fujiko navamwe vazhinji .
Sezvaunoshandisa zvaunodzidza muBhaibheri , uchawana kuti ukama hwako naMwari hahuzati huchizokuvadzika bedzi asi ukama hwako naMwari nomunhu ari wose ari pauri huchadarowo , kubatanidza nehama dzako dzomuroorano .
Uchawana izvo Bhaibheri rinopikira , ndiko kuti , “ rugare rwaMwari runopfuura mufungo wose . ” — VaFiripi 4 : 6 , 7 .
Fujiko navamwe vadudzwa munyaya dzino vakasvika pakufarikanya rugare rwakadaro — unogonawo kudaro .
Hungu , kupfurikidza nokuvimba naJehovha Mwari nokutevera zano reShoko rake , Bhaibheri , iwewo unogona kuvaka ndokuchengeta ushamwari hunofadza nehama dzako dzomuroorano .
