Murume — Muyananisi Here Kana Kuti Imharadzi ?
Apo zvizvarwa zviviri kana kuti zvitatu zvinogara muimba imwe cheteyo , basa romurume mukuchengeta rugare rwemhuri harizati richifanira kufuratirwa .
Pamusoro pomurume akadaro anonzvenga mutoro wake , Purofesa Tohru Arichi wapaYunivhesiti yeKyushu , mazvikokota muruzivo rwamagariro avanhu , anonyora , kuti :
“ Apo vanyakuroorana vanogara na [ amai ] , amai vanofunga zvinodikanwa zvomwanakomana wavo , uye nomutoo usati uri wamaune vanotarisira mwanakomana wavo apo ivo vanocherekedza zvinoshaikwa zvakadaro .
Mwanakomana anogamuchira tarisiro yakadaro pasina zenguriro ipi neipi .
Kudai mwanakomana aizofunga zvakati kurei nezvomugariro womudzimai wake ndokuisa amai vake munzvimbo yake pamusoro pokupindira kwavo , chinetsocho chingapedzwa .
Nomutoo unosuruvarisa uye kazhinji kazhinji zvikuru kwazvo , mwanakomana haazati achitongocherekedza ikoko . ”
Ko zvino , murume anogona sei kuita basa rokushingaira mukuita rugare mumhuri yake ?
Mitsuharu anotaura kuti kushandisa kwake nheyo dzeBhaibheri kwakabetsera mhuri yake .
“ Chisungo pakati paamai nomwanakomana wavo chakasimba zvikuru kunyange zvazvo iye akura kuva mukuru , ” iye anobvuma kudaro , “ naizvozvo mwana anofanira kuita nhamburiko yokuitira hanya ‘ kusiya baba vake naamai vake ndokunamatira kumudzimai wake . ’ ”
Akashandisa nheyo kupfurikidza nokukurukura nhau pamusoro petarisirwo yavana nerovedzwo inoitwa bedzi nomudzimai wake , uye iye haana kuenzanisa mudzimai wake naamai vake pakwakauya pabasa rapamba .
“ Zvino , ” iye anopfuurira , “ isu navabereki vangu tinoremekedzana .
Mumwe nomumwe anoziva apo kupindira kuchava kunoshatirisa uye apo betsero nebatira pamwe zvichava zvichaongwa . ”
Mukuwedzera kuku‘namatira kumudzimai wake ’ murume anofanira kuva mureveri pakati paamai vake nomudzimai wake .
Anoda kuva muteereri akanaka uye kuvaita kuti vadurure mwoyo yavo .
Mumwe murume , uyo akadzidza kutarisira migariro mukuchenjera , anotanga kuwana kuti mudzimai wake anonzwa sei .
Ipapo , mudzimai wake aripo , iye anotaura naamai vake pamusoro penhau dzinobatanidzwa .
Kupfurikidza nokudarokwo kuita basa rake somuyananisi , mwanakomana anogona kubetsera kuparira ukama hunofadza mumusha pakati pavakadzi vaviri vaanoda .
