Chaunofanira Kuziva Pamusoro Pengirozi
“ Vadzidzi vorudzidziso vane 3 000 vakaungana muNew York kwamazuva mana vhiki rakapera kuti vanzwe mishumo inopfuura 500 inoreva nezvemisoro inovambira padonzo remisere mumharidzo kusvikira kuukoshi hwomuitiro worudzidziso kumitezo yePentecostal .
Hakuno munhu akadudza ngirozi . ” — Daily News , December 26 , 1982 .
NHASI , makore masere gare gare , vafundisi vachiri kutaura zvishoma pamusoro pengirozi .
Neiko ?
Kungava here kuti ava vatumwa vokudenga vanongorangarirwawo zvavo bedzi sorutivi rwengano yekare ?
Kana kuti variko chaizvoizvo here ?
Kana zvakadaro , chii chaunofanira kuziva pamusoro pavo ?
Dziriko Here ?
Ngirozi hadzizati dzichingovawo zvadzo “ ubati ushe ” kana kuti “ masangano enzvimbo yose , ” sokutaura kunoita vamwe vazivi .
Zvamazvirokwazvo dzinoringanira kududzwa kane mazana muShoko raMwari , Bhaibheri .
Mumitauro yapakuvamba yeBhaibheri , mashoko anoshandurwa kuva “ ngirozi ” ( chiHebheru , mal·ʼakhʹ ; chiGiriki , agʹge·los ) chaizvoizvo anoreva “ uyo anounza shoko ” kana kuti kungoti bedzi “ mutumwa . ”
Aya mashoko anowanika kanenge kane 400 muBhaibheri rose , dzimwe nguva achinongedzera kumunhu , asi kazhinji kazhinji kuvatumwa vomudzimu .
Ngirozi yakaoneka kumudzimai asingabereki waManoa ichizivisa kunamba mimba yomwanakomana wake , Samsoni , yakanga iri chaiyoiyo kwaari .
Ndozvakanga zvakaitawo ngirozi nhatu dzakaoneka kuna Abrahama nomudzimai wake Sara , uye mbiri dzakabudisa Roti , uye iya yakagara pasi pomuti mukuru ikataura naGidheoni .
Panguva yokuberekwa kwaJesu , ngirozi yakaoneka kamwe kamwe kuboka ravafudzi iri pakati pechiedza chinoteya meso , nechinon’animira . — Ruka 2 : 8 , 9 .
Ngizori idzedzo dzaiva chaidzoidzo .
Dzakanga dzisiri mufungo wokuzviitira kana kuti simba risiri romunhu .
Dzaiita donzo rakapiwa savatumwa vanobva kuna Mwari , uye nhauro dzacho dzakanyorwa nomutoo wakakodzera muBhaibheri nokuda kwebetsero yedu nhasi .
Nokudaro Bhaibheri rinozivisa udzame hunokosha pamusoro pengirozi hwaunodikanirwa kuziva , humwe hwacho hunorwisana nemifungo yegamuchidzanwa .
Dzakadiniko ?
Zvimwe ungafananidzira ngirozi navakadzi vakaisvotsvinda kana kuti zvisikwa zvakwegura , zvakafanana navana zvine mapapiro , zvinonyemwerera zvakanaka zvakapfeka nguvo chena , zvinoridza hudimbwa huduku , zvinotapatira mumhepo .
Kana zvakadaro , unofanira kuziva kuti iyi mifungo isino kururama yakatorwa mumifungo yechihedheni , yakadai sengano yechiGiriki .
Kana kuti mifungoyo yakagamuchirwa pashure pokunge kunyorwa kweBhaibheri kwapera .
Muzviono zvokufananidzira zveBhaibheri , zvisikwa zvomudzimu zvakadai samaserafimi namakerubhi zvina mapapiro . — Isaya 6 : 2 ; Ezekieri 10 : 5 ; Zvakazarurwa 14 : 6 .
Shoko raMwari rinorondedzera ngirozi kuva semidzimu ine simba zvikuru , uye mudzimu hauoneki .
Yakanga iri “ ngirozi yaJehovha ” yakauraya vaAsiria vane 185 000 mumusasa womuvengi waIsraeri muusiku humwe chete !
Apo ngirozi dzaizviratidzira dzimene kuvanhu , dzaigarooneka savanhu vakapfeka zvakakwana , kwete savakadzi kana kuti vana uye dzisati dzichitongova muchimiro chohunhu chakaderera .
Ko izvi zvisikwa zvomudzimu zvine simba zvakabva kupi ?
Bhaibheri rinoti “ kupfurikidza naye [ Jesu ] zvimwe zvinhu zvose zvakasikwa zviri mumatenga uye pamusoro papasi , zvinhu zvinooneka nezvinhu zvisingaoneki . ”
Jehovha Mwari , kupfurikidza nouyu Mwanakomana dangwe , haana kungosika bedzi ngirozi kare kare pamberi pomunhu asi akadziitawo kuti dzive muchimiro chakakwirira zvikuru choupenyu kupfuura munhu . — Jobho 38 : 4 , 7 ; 2 Petro 2 : 11 .
Dzino Hunhu Here ?
Ngirozi , savanhu , dzine kunzwa .
Pashure pokuona kusikwa kwapasi , tinoudzwa kuti ngirozi “ dzakadanidzira nomufaro pamwe chete , ” kunyange “ kudanidzira murumbidzo . ”
Bhaibheri rinozivisawo kuti “ mufaro unomuka pakati pengirozi dzaMwari pamusoro pomuiti wechivi anopfidza . ”
Zvamazvirokwazvo , hakuna “ simba ” risiri romunhu ringadai rakafarikanya mufaro mukuru unorondedzerwa mundima idzodzo .
Ngirozi dzine ganhurirowo .
