Iva ane chokwadi chokuti betsero yomutsa ichakupiwa . — Jakobho 5 : 14 , 15 .
Kungavawo kwokuti dzimwe chinjo dzinodikanwa munzira yaunobata nayo vabereki vako kana kuti yaunorangarira nayo zano rinobva kuvakuru vechiKristu , kunyange nzira yaunosarudza nayo shamwari .
Kungava kusiri nyore kuita chinjo dzakadaro , asi Zvirevo 11 : 19 , ( NW ) inotiyeuchidza , kuti : “ Uyo anomira zvakatsiga nokuda kwokururama anowana upenyu , asi uyo unodzingana nezvakaipa unowana rufu rwake amene . ”
Jehovha anoda kuti uve akakwana here ?
Nyangwe .
“ Ndianiko anogona kutaura , kuti : ‘ Ndakachenura mwoyo wangu ; ndakava akachena pachivi changu ’ ? ” inobvunza kudaro Zvirevo 20 : 9 .
( NW ) Zvatiri vasina kukwana , tichiri vakakombamira kukuita mhosho .
Bva nokuda kworudzikinuro rwaKristu , tinogona kurambira muchimiro chakanaka naMwari .
Somuenzaniso , pwere inorwa zvakasimba kudzivisa muitiro wakashata , wakadai somuitiro usina kuchena webonhora , haidikanirwi kufunga kuti iyo haikwaniriswi hayo nokuda kworubhapatidzo .
* Zvamazvirokwazvo , kupfurikidza nokudzivisa kwakasimba zvikuru kusarurama , munhu anogona kuita kuti mwoyo waJehovha ufare ! — Zvirevo 27 : 11 .
‘ Ndati Ndaita Mwari Shamwari Yangu Here ? ’
Zvimwe mubvunzo unoisvokosha zvikuru , kunyange zvazvo zvakadaro , unobatanidza ukama hwako naMwari .
Yeuka : Unozvitsaurira umene , kusati kuri kubasa kana kuti kuchiito , kana kuti kunyange kusangano , asi kuna Mwari iye amene .
Ko Mwari anoratidzika kuva asi mupenyu , ari kure here ?
Kana kuti wati wamuziva here ndokumuda soMunhu ?
Kana zvakadaro , uchazviwana umene uchitaura naye kazhinji kazhinji , neisati iri karukano kwaitika , asi kuchibva pamwoyo . — Pisarema 62 : 8 .
Uchazviwanawo umene uchigombedzerwa chose chose kutaura navamwe pamusoro paMwari .
( Enzanisa 2 VaKorinte 5 : 14 . )
Zvirevo 15 : 7 ( NW ) inoti : “ Miromo yavakachenjera inoramba ichiparadzira zivo pose pose . ”
Uri kuita kudaro kupfurikidza nokugaroparidzira kuna vamwe here ?
Kana kuti uri kubvumira hako nhandaro , varaidzo , kana kuti kunyange usimbe kukudzivisa kubetsera vamwe kuziva Mwari here ? — Zvirevo 19 : 24 .
Hungu , kuti rubhapatidzo rugova nerevo , Mwari anofanira kuva shamwari yako chaiyoiyo zvikuru .
( Enzanisa Jakobho 2 : 23 . )
Kana ikoku kusati kwakadaro zvino , mhaka haizati iri yaMwari , nokuti iye anokoka noushamwari vose kumutsvaka .
Uye kupfurikidza nokusimbirira mufundo yomunhu oga , munyengetero , uye kusonganirana navanhu vake , mukufambira mberi kwenguva uchanzwa kuva pedyo zvikuru naMwari .
Rubhapatidzo ruchava muuyo womuzvarirwo wo‘kuswedera pedyo kwakadaro kuna Mwari . ’ — Jakobho 4 : 8 .
Somuenzaniso , rangarira imwe mhandara inonzi Cindy .
Inonyora , kuti : “ Ndakabhapatidzwa pazera ramakore 14 .
Ndinoziva kuti kuva anozengurira kwakadini pamusoro pokuita kudaro .
Asi ndinoda kutaura kuti ndichinhu chakaisvonaka zvikuru chaunogona kuita .
Funga hako , kuziva kuti Jehovha akakutendera uye kuti ‘ haazati achizotongokusiya kana kuti kukurega ’ !
Kudai munhu upi noupi aizondibvunza kana iye achifanira kuzvitsaurira amene kuna Jehovha , ndaizoti hungu !
Asika rega kukuitira kufadza mumwe munhuwo zvake .
Kuite nokuti unoda kukuita . ”
[ Mashoko Omuzasi ]
Ona inoti “ Ndinofanira Kubhapatidzwa Here ? ” inoteverwa neino muchinyorwa chino chaMukai !
