Kunzvera Mhuka — Muitiro Wekare
KUSHANDISWA kwakapararira kwemhuka navanachiremba navezvesayenzi kuti vanzwisise kushanda kwomuviri wavanhu hakuzi kwechienzi kuzana rino rechi 20 ramakore .
Mhuka dzave dzichishandiswa mukunzvera kwokurapa kwaanenge makore 2 000 .
Muzana rechitatu ramakore P.N.V . , muAlexandria , Egipita , zvinyorwa zvinoratidzira kuti Erasistratus muzivi uye wezvesayenzi aishandisa mhuka kudzidza kushanda kwomuviri uye akakuwana kuva kunoshanda kuvanhu .
Muzana rechina ramakore , Aristotle nyanzvi yechiGiriki akawana kupfurikidza nokufundwa kwemhuka mashoko anokosha pamusoro pokuumbwa nokushanda kwomuviri womunhu .
Makore ana mazana mashanu gare gare chiremba wechiGiriki Galen akashandisa maape nenguruve kubvumikisa dzidziso yake yokuti tsinga dzinofambisa ropa panzvimbo pemhepo .
Kunzvera Mhuka — Kuita Kwamasimba Masimba
KUDAI chiverengero chaichoicho chezvisikwa zvinamakumbo mana chinoshandiswa mukuedza kwamarabhorotari uye semienzaniso nokuda kwokunzvera kwokurapa chingarongwa , hwerengedzo yose yegore negore ingava inokatyamadza .
Kunokarakadzwa kuti dzinenge mhuka dzinamamirioni 17 — imbwa , katsi , maprimate , mbira , uye tsuro — dzinoshandiswa gore rimwe nerimwe muUnited States moga bedzi .
Makonzo nembeva zvinoita 85 muzana yeichi chiverengero .
Sezvakusina zvinyorwa zvakarurama zvouko idzi mhuka dzinoshandiswa kana kuti ingani , izvi zviverengero zvinorangarirwa namamwe magorokotera kuva zviverengero zvisina kutsarukana zvikurusa .
Mamwe manyuko anoisa chiverengero chose nokuda kweUnited States pakuva chiri pedyo zvikuru namamirioni ane zana .
Unowana izvi zviverengero kuva zvinokatyamadza here ?
Kunyange zvazvo kubayirwa kweizvi zvisikwa zvine mvere kwave kusati kuri kusina donzo , unovhundutswa nomufungowo zvawo wakwo here ?
Unorangarira uku kuuraya kuva kwakashata here ?
Mamirioni avanhu anovenga kushandiswa kwemhuka mukunzvera .
Vamwe vanotaura kuti kushandiswa zvisinokufanira kwemhuka rusarura mhuka .
Wezvokusarura mhuka ndimumwe ano “ rerekera kufariro dzorudzi rwake amene uye mukurwisana nefariro dzamamwe marudzi . ”
( Point / Counterpoint Responses to Typical pro - Vivisection Arguments ) Mukuwirirana navezvokusunungurwa kwemhuka , vezvokusarura mhuka vano “ davira kuti miuyo inoruramisa mitoo yacho , uye kuti chakaipa chinofanira kuitwa [ kumhuka ] kuwana chakanaka [ nokuda kwavanhu ] . ”
Kuno rumwe rutivi , murangariro wesayenzi unopetwa mumibvunzo inotevera : Unoitira pfunde pfunde gadziriro inoreverera kuuraiwa kwemhuka zvikuru zvokuti vanachiremba vangadzidza zivo itsva mukuita kuvhiya vanhu kana kuti kudzivisa kupararira kwehosha here ?
Wakagadzirira kurega mirimo mitsva inoponesa upenyu nemishonga nemhaka yokuti unoziva kuti iyo yakatanga kuedzwa pamhuka here ?
Ungadisisa here , hungu kuda , kuita kuti uropi hwakaremara hwomwana wako kana kuti mubereki mupenyu hushandiswe mukuedza kwokuvhiya panzvimbo pemhuka ?
Uye pakupedzisira , pane ichi : Kana kunzvera mhuka kuchigona kukuponesa kana kuti mudikanwi pahosha inorwadza zvikuru kana kuti rufu , waizokuramba here uine murangariro wokuti kubayira mhuka kuti munhu aponeswe kwakashata ?
Vamwe vangataura havo kuti chinetso chacho hachiziri nyore zvikuru kugadzikisa .
Sangano Rokusunungura Mhuka
Hunganyuvezvo , mukati mamakore gumi omuma 1980 , kwakanga kuno mufungo waiwedzera wokushandiswa kwemhuka mukunzvera .
Nhasi mufungo iwowo wakashandurwa kuva boka renyika yose ramasangano anoshingaira anopfuurira kuwedzera musimba nomuzviverengero .
Anotaura zvikuru mukuraira kubviswa chose chose kwokushandiswa kwemhuka dzose nokuda kwokuedza kwokurapa kana kuti kwerabhorotari .
Vezvokushingairira maruramiro emhuka vari kuita kuti kutaura kwavo kunzwike kupfurikidza nokuratidzira kwomumakona emigwagwa , kupesvedzera kwezvamatongerwe enyika , magazini namapepanhau , nhepfenyuro neterevhizheni , uye , nomutoo unoisvocherekedzwa , unyanzvi hwokurwa uye masimba masimba .
Mumwe wezvokushingaira akatanhamara weCanada akataura pamusoro pesangano rerusununguko , kuti : “ Riri kupararira nomutoo wokukurumidza muEurope yose , Australia neNew Zealand .
Nyika dzeStates dziri kuramba dzichisimba zvikuru kwazvo .
MuCanada munewedzero inokatyamadza .
Kune boka ramasangano rakapararira munyika yose uye muitiro mumburumbwa yose iri nokuda kwokutsigirwa kwamasangano amaruramiro emhuka anodenha zvikuru . ”
Dzimwe aaya ‘ mapoka anodenha ’ ari kushandisa masimba masimba mukutsigira nzira yawo .
Mukati mamakore mashomanene okupedzisira , anenge marabhorotari 25 okunzverera muUnited States akapwanywa namapoka amaruramiro emhuka .
Marabhorotari apaYunivhesiti akabhombwa .
Uku kuvhojokera kwakaparira kuvadziko inokosha madhora ana mamirioni .
Zvinyorwa zvinokosha namashoko anokosha zvakaparadzwa .
Mhuka dziri kunzverwa dzakabiwa ndokusunungurwa .
Mune chinoitika chimwe chakadaro , kunzvera kwakakosha pamusoro poupofu hwavacheche kwakaparadzwa .
Midziyo inodhura zvikurusa yakawanwa kuva inokosha mazana ezviuru zvamadhora yakaputswa .
Mutsamba yokutsutsumwa yakatumirwa kuvakuru vakuru vapayunivhesiti namanyuko enhau , rimwe boka rinorwisa rakaganza kuti kuparadza mabheko anoita $ 10 000 muanenge masekondi 12 nomugwara wesimbi we $ 5 kwakanga kuri “ muuyo wakanaka zvikuru patsigiro yedu . ”
Mune dzimwe nzvimbo vanzveri , vanachiremba navezvesayenzi vakawana ropa rakaduririrwa pamipakwa napamashoko okunzvera napazviratidzo zvaverabhorotari zvakapendwa nomuchina wokupenda nawo pamadziro .
Mumwe mushumo unotaura nezvo “ kunetswa , kubatanidza netyisidziro dzorufu , dzavezvesayenzi nemhuri dzavo . ”
MuUnited States , vezvokusunungurwa kwemhuka vakabudisa tyisidziro dzinopfuura gumi nembiri dzorufu kana kuti masimba masimba kuna vezvesayenzi vamwe navamwe .
Muna 1986 nhepfenyuro yeLondon BBC , mumwe mutsinhiri akati : “ Chinobatanidza vezvokushingaira ndiko kupwiswa kwokuti chiito chakananga — kuparadzwa kwepfuma , uye kunyange upenyu ihwo humene — kunoruramiswa mutsika muhondo yokusunungura mhuka . ”
Mumwe mutungamiriri wokusunungurwa kwemhuka , akati : “ Kwave kusati kune munhu upi noupi akakuvadzwa asi iyeyo ityisidziro ine ngozi . . .
Nokukurumidza zvikurusa mumwe munhu acharova shure uye pangava nekuvadziko pavanhu . ”
Muna 1986 , mubvunzurudzo imwe cheteyo , mutungamiriri akadeya kutaura masimba masimba muBritain neWest Germany .
Zvinoitika muchimiro chokubhomba nemwoto namasimba masimba zvakabvumikisa kudeya kutaura kwake .
MuUnited States , nhamburiko dzakatoitwa paupenyu hwomumwe munhu ane kambani inonzvera mhuka .
Chiito chokukurumidza chamapurisa chakamuponesa pakuva anobhombwa .
Zvisinei , handi vezvokusunungura mhuka vose vanobvumirana nouhu unyanzvi hwamasimba masimba , husati huri hwapamutemo .
Neiko Pane Chishoro Chavo ?
Mukuwirirana neThe Journal of the American Medical Association , “ vanhu vazhinjisa vanoitira hanya kushandiswa kwemhuka mukunzverwa kwokushanda kwomushonga mumuviri kunogona kukamuranisirwa mumapoka maviriwo zvawo : ( 1 ) avo vanoitira hanya garikano yemhuka vasingashori kunzverwa kwokushanda kwomushonga mumuviri asi vanoda simbisiro yokuti mhuka dzinobatwa nomutoo womutsa sezvingabvira , kuti chiverengero chemhuka dzinoshandiswa chive chiduku chinobvira chinodikanwa , uye kuti mhuka dzinoshandiswa bedzi apo kunova kuri madikanwa . ”
Iri boka , mukuwirirana neiyi nzvero yazvino uno , rinoita kutaura kushoma kwavoruzhinji .
Boka rechipiri , mukuwirirana namanyuko mamwe chetewo , “ avo vanoitira hanya maruramiro emhuka vanoshandisa chimiro chikuru chokuchinja uye vanoshora chose chose kushandiswa kwemhuka mukunzverwa kwokushanda kwomushonga mumuviri . ”
“ Mhuka dzina maruramiro apakuvamba asingaparadzanisiki , ” akadaro mutarisiri biyamwe weboka rimwe rakadaro .
“ Kana mhuka ine simba rokunzwa kurwadziwa kana kuti kutya , ipapo ina maruramiro okuita kuti zvinhu izvozvo zvirege kuitwa pairi . ”
“ Hapana hwaro hwokuva nomufungo nokuda kwokutaura kuti munhu ana maruramiro chaiwo , ” mumwe mutauriri akataura kudaro .
“ Zvose zvakafanana .
Zvose ndezvomuboka rakakwirira rezvisikwa . ”
Vezvokusunungurwa kwemhuka vazhinji vanopwiswa zvikurukuru vanoshora kushandiswa kwemhuka nokuda kwezvokudya , zvokupfeka , mitambo , uye kunyange zvipfuyo zvokutamba nazvo .
Varedzi vakasundumidzirwa mumvura naavo vanoshora kubatwa nokudyiwa kwehove .
Vanhu vanopfeka mabhachi ane mvere nezvipfeko zveganda remhuka vakatukwa pamigwagwa .
Zvitoro zvakapwanywa uye mabhachi anodhura emvere achiparadzwa naavo vano murangariro wokuchinja zvikuru wokushandiswa kwemhuka nokubatwa zvisinokufanira .
“ Handizati ndichizodya mazai nokuda kwezvokudya zvamagwanani kana kuti kupfeka zvipfeko zvamakanda , ” mumwe akataura kudaro .
“ Kunenge seri kwenhindi iri yose yebacon uye zai riri rose rinoratidzika kuva risingakuvadzi , ” rakanyevera kudaro pepanhau reHumane Society of the United States , kwa “ kavanda nhau refu , yakavanzika yokutambura kusingatsungiririki . ”
Richipedzisa nemifananidzo yenguruve nehuku zvakapfigirwa muzvirugu zviduku nezvizumba , pepanhau rakapomera kuti iyi migariro , yakapararira zvikuru munzvimbo dzamabasa dzinogadzirwa zvinhu nokugadzirwa kwenyama yenguruve neyehuku , inoita “ ndiro yenyama yenguruve namazai haisati iri chimwe chinhu kunze kwe‘kudya kwamangwanani kwoutsinye . ’ ”
Sezvinooneka , kunokunzwa kwakasimba nokwapachokwadi kunobatanidzwa mukudzivirirwa kwamaruramiro emhuka .
Nhau Dzinotyisa
Vanhu vazhinji vanodavira kuti kushora kunzvera mhuka kunoruramiswa zvizere .
Imwe yenhau dzinomukurumbira wakashata zvikuru yakabatanidzwa muRabhorotari Rokukuvara Musoro rapayunivhesiti yakakurumbira yeAmerica .
Matepi evhidhio akabiwa akatorwa mukati mokuvhojokera kwokusunungurwa kwemhuka akaratidzira “ tsoko dzichidzvanyidzirwa misoro yadzo mumuchina unorovanya nesimba , vanzveri vachiseka kuita kwokupfizuka kwezvisikwa zvine uropi hwakuvadzwa , ” yakashuma kudaro magazini yeKiwanis yaSeptember 1988 .
Ikoku kwakaparira kubviswa kwokuwanira mari kwehurumende nokuda kwerabhorotari .
Uyewo kune kuedza kwakashata kweDraize , kwakanyanyofanana zvikuru nokwenzvimbo dzamabasa anogadzirwa zvinhu ecosmetic , shampoo , detergent , uye lye .
Uyu muedzo unoshandiswa kuyera kuswinya kwomushonga ungapinda mumeso omunhu .
Chaizvoizvo , kubvira patsuro dzinopfuiwa nhanhatu kusvikira kupfumbamwe dzinoiswa munzvimbo dzinobvumira bedzi misoro yadzo nemitsipa kubuda kunze .
Ikoku kunodzidzivisa kukwenga meso adzo nenzara pashure pokunge mushonga wadururirwa madziri .
Kuri kushumwa kuti tsuro dzinonjiririka mukurwadziwa .
Kunyange vanzveri vazhinji vanoshora zvikurukuru ichi chimiro chokuedza uye vari kuedza kudzivisa kushandiswa kwacho .
Masangano amaruramiro emhuka akatsigira nhau zhinji dzinotyisa dzinoitwa mumarabhorotari okunzvera mhuka .
Vezvokusunungurwa kwemhuka havana mufungo wakakwirira waDr .
Robert White anokorwa mashoko kare .
American Anti - Vivisection Society yakanyora kuti iye “ munzveri wemhuka akashata wokuCleveland uyo akaisira misoro yetsoko uye akachengeta uropi hwetsoko huri hupenyu mumvura , kunze kwomuviri . ”
Sezvinoitika mupokanidzano zhinji , pane kunyanyisa kuviri , uye pane nzira yapakati inoedza kutora zvakanakisisa ndokubvisa zvakaipisisa zvemiuyo .
Somuenzaniso , kuna mapindukiro api naapi anoshanda pakuedza nemhuka here ?
Ko kurambwa chose chose kwokunzvera mhuka ndikwo bedzi mhinduro inoshanda , yakadzikama here ?
Nyaya yedu inotevera icharangarira iyi mibvunzo .
