Mirangariro Inosiana
“ NDINODAVIRA kuti mhuka dzina maruramiro ayo , kunyange zvazvo akasiana needu timene , akaita saasingabvisiki .
Ndinodavira kuti mhuka dzinamaruramiro okusava namarwadzo , kutya kana kuti kurwadziswa mumuviri kunoitwa padziri nesu . . . .
Dzinamaruramiro okusaitirwa utsinye munzira ipi neipi samanyuko ezvokudya , nokuda kwevaraidzo kana kuti rimwe donzo ripi neripi . ” — Naturalist Roger Caras , ABC - TV News , U.S.A . ( Newsweek , December 26 , 1988 ) .
“ Kutarira pamufananidzo mukuru , handigoni kufuratira mwero mukurusa wezvakanaka zvakaparirwa nokunzvera .
Majekiseni , kurapa , unyanzvi hwokuvhiya , uye miitiro yakatangwa mumarabhorotari zvakawedzera nduramo nomutoo unokatyamadza muzana ramakore rakapfuura . . .
Mune iyi tsananguro , kusashandisa mhuka nokuda kwokunzvera kunogona kuonwa sechisarudzo choutsinye : Takava nenzira yokudzidza mapodzerwe ehosha asi hatina kuishandisa . ” — Marcia Kelly , Health Sciences , Fall 1989 , University of Minnesota .
“ Ndinoti ‘ Aiwa ’ kukunzverwa kwemhuka .
Kwete bedzi nokuda kwetsika , asi zvikurukuru nokuda kwezvikonzero zvesayenzi .
Kwakaratidzirwa kuti miuyo inobva mukunzverwa kwemhuka haizati ichitongoshanda kuvanhu .
Kune mutemo womusikirwo wakabatana namavakirwe anoitwa muviri nezvinodyiwa . . . mukuwirirana nokushanda kwomushonga mumuviri , uko kwakasimbiswa nokuda kworudzi rumwe , kunoshanda bedzi nokuda kworudzi irworwo chairwo uye kwete nokuda kworumwe . . . .
Kunzverwa kwemhuka ndokwokurangarira kusina kururama , kusina maturo , kunodhura uye kupfuurirazve kwoutsinye . ” — Gianni Tamino , munzveri wapaYunivhesiti yePadua , chikoro chikuru chemishonga cheItaly .
