Kunzvera Mhuka — Murangariro Wakadzikama
KUNYANGE zvazvo mutengo unoripirwa ungava unomutsa nharo , vanhu vazhinji vanodavira kuti kunzvera mhuka kwakaparira zvakanaka zvikurusa nokuda kwavanhu .
Kunyange avo vanoreverera masimba masimba mukurwisana nokushandiswa kwokuedzwa kwemhuka vave vari vabetserwi vezivo itsva yokurapa nemiitiro yokurapa uyewo mirimo inorwisa hosha .
Martin Stephens weHumane Society yeUnited States akati : “ Tinotofanira hedu kuva vakatendeseka ndokuziva kuti kwave kune betsero dzakati kuti dzinobva mukunzvera mhuka .
Asika nharidzano yedu yokupedzisira ndikwo kutsiviwa kwakakwana kwemhuka .
( Parade Magazine , October 9 , 1988 ) “ Ndinobvuma , ” akadaro Vicki Miller , purezidhendi weToronto Humane Society , “ kuti zvakanaka zvakati kuti zvakaitwa nemhuka mukuvamba mezana ramakore .
Kudzorwa kwehosha yeshuga kwakawanwa nomutoo uno mufungo mukunzvera mhuka .
Asika hapana dikanwo yakwo zvino nokuti tine marudzi ose oruzivo rwounyanzvi hwamapinduko . ” — The Sunday Star , Toronto , Canada .
Uyu mutsoropodzi mumwe cheteyo akabvunzwa mapindurire aaizoita avo vanopokanidza : Kana gonzo richifanira kufa kuti riponese upenyu hwomwana , kwakarifanira .
Kana mhuka dzichichengetwa kuti dzirege kunzverwa , vana vanofa kuti vaponese makonzo .
Mhinduro yake kuToronto Globe and Mail yakanga iri yokuti : “ Inongova hayo nhau yendangariro , uye mumurangariro iwowo kwave kuchidokuva kusingabviri kukurira . . .
Pane pokanidzano yegonzo nomwana uye nguva yose unorashikirwa . ”
Mubvunzo wakabvunzwa munyaya inotangireyi , kuti : “ Kana kunzvera mhuka kuchigona kukuponesa kana kuti mudikanwi pahosha inorwadza kana kuti rufu , ungakuramba here ? ”
John Kaplan , purofesa womutemo wapaStanford University , California , akanyora mhinduro muchinyorwa chaNovember 1988 chemagazini yeScience , kuti : “ Avo vanoshora kunzvera mhuka havawanzomira panheyo ndokurairidza vanachiremba vavo kusashandisa miuyo yokunzvera kushanda kwomushonga mumuviri pamhuka apo ikwo kungabetsera vadikanwi vavo kana kuti ivo vamene .
Uyewo ivo vave vasati vachidisisa kuzvirambira ivo vamene zvimuko zveenderero mberi zvipi nezvipi zvomunguva yemberi zvinobva mukunzvera mhuka .
Tinogona kuyemura nheyo dzinogombedzera Zvapupu zvaJehovha kuramba kuisirwa ropa . . . naavo vanoramba kuvhimwa kwemhuka dzine mvere kusapfeka zvipfeko zvine mvere .
Asi tinofanira kurwisa nesimba pfungwa inoparira avo vanoshora kunzvera mhuka kutevera nzira yavo kwete kupfurikidza nomuenzaniso asi panzvimbo pakwo kupfurikidza nokurwisa mupokanidzano dzokusatendeseka dzokunyima munhu ari wose betsero . ”
“ Vanhu vanofanira kuziviswa , ” akanyora kudaro mupepeti wenhau wemagazini yeScience yaMarch 10 , 1989 , “ kuti kunzvera pamhuka kunobetserawo dzimwe mhuka .
Chokwadi , jekiseni rehosha yen’ombe , utachiona hunouraya mamirioni en’ombe pashoma napashoma uye inorwadza , rakatangwa kupfurikidza nokunzvera mhuka ; jekiseniro zvino riri kushandiswa neWorld Health Organization kumamirioni en’ombe muAfrica . ”
Murangariro weBhaibheri
Pashure paMafashamo emburumbwa yose muzuva raNoa , Jehovha Mwari akabudisa chirevo kuna Noa nokuvana vake , avo vanobatanidza chizvarwa chedu : “ Mhuka iri yose inofamba iri mhenyu ingabatira sezvokudya zvenyu . Kana zviri zvinomera zvakasvibira , ndinozvipa kwamuri .
Nyama bedzi nomweya wayo — ropa rayo — hamuzati muchifanira kudya . ”
Makanda emhuka aigonawo kuva anoshandiswa nokuda kwezvokupfeka .
Ikoku hakungaputsi udzori hwakapiwa naMwari hwomunhu pamhuka . — Genesi 3 : 21 .
“ Kana mhuka dzingashandiswa sezvokudya zvinotsigira upenyu hwavanhu , ” yakanyora kudaro magazini yaMukai !
yaJune 22 , 1980 , “ kunoratidzika kuva kuno mufungo kudzishandisa mukunzvera kwokurapa kuponesa upenyu .
Zvisinei , irworwu harwuzati rwuri rubvumidzo rwokunzvera kusingaganhurirwi uye kazhinji kazhinji kusina maturo , kwokudzokorora kunobatanidza kutambura kukuru . ”
Zvamazvirokwazvo , kubva mumurangariro weBhaibheri , utsinye hukurusa kumhuka hahungagoni kururamiswa . — Eksodho 23 : 4 , 5 , 12 ; Dheuteronomio 25 : 4 ; Zvirevo 12 : 10 .
Vanachiremba vazhinji navezvesayenzi vanobvuma kuti zvakanaka zvakati kuti zvakabva musangano rokuchinja raavo vanoshora kunzvera mhuka . “ Chitsama chinotyisa chamapfundo akaitwa nesangano regarikano yemhuka ndeokunyanyisa asi akarurama hawo , ” akabvuma kudaro mumwe wezvesayenzi .
“ Upenyu nokutambura kwemhuka zvechokwadi zvinofanira kurangarirwa nokuda kwechimwe chinhu , ” akazivisa kudaro wezvesayenzi weAmerica Jeremy J .
Stone .
“ Zivo yakati kuti inogona kuwanwa pamutengo wakanyanyokwirira kwazvo , ” yakabvuma kudaro nyanzvi yokushanda kwomuviri Dr .
D .
H .

Smith .
“ Tinobvuma nechishuvo chokuita kuti kunzvera kuve kunorwadza zvishoma , kutarisira uye kuderedza chiverengero chemhuka mukunzvera , ” akadaro Dr .
J .
B .
Wyngaarden weU.S . National Institutes of Health .
Uye mumwe wezvokushingaira wemhuka akabvuma , kuti : “ Kwaichimbova hunenge ushingi kushandisa uye kusafunga chinhu chipi nechipi pamusoro pakwo .
Nhasi , kufunga pamusoro pamapinduko kunorangarirwa kuva chinhu chokuita . ”
“ Mapanduko ” ishoko gurusa .
Vezvesayenzi vanobvuma kuti havangatongosviki papfundo rokubvisa chose chose kunzvera mhuka , asi kwakunobvira vanoramba vachitsvaka mapinduko .
Somuenzaniso , tsuro hadzisati dzichashandiswazve kusimbisa mimba yomunhu , sezvo muitiro wokusimbisa nawo zvino uri kuwanikwa .
Mbira hadzisati dzichashandiswazve kuwana utachiona hworurindi .
Mitoo yokuwana nayo hosha zvino iri kuponesa upenyu hweidzi mhuka idzo dzingadai dzakafa nomumwe mutoo .
Mimwe miitiro yokunzvera nayo yakatsiva kunzvera pambeva .
Uye tsuro zhinji dzaifukidzirwa namahwendefa nokuda kwokunzvera kunorwadza kweDraize dzingaregwa nokuda kwebinduko rokushandisa rukanda rwezai renhunzvi yehuku sorukanda rwapamusoro rwokunzvera narwo .
Zvamazvirokwazvo , vanhu vanotapurika nokutambura kwemhuka vanokarira kuti kuchava namamwe mabinduko mazhinji anowanwa , uye nokukurumidza .
Zvisinei , binduko gurusa rokunzvera mhuka richava Paradhiso iya yapasi yanguve ichimirirwa iyo maKristu echokwadi ave achinyengeterera .
Jehovha Mwari , Musiki ano rudo , akavimbisa kuti zvirwere zvose uye rufu irwo rwumene zvichaparadzwa nokusingaperi .
Munyika itsva yakavimbiswa yaMwari , munhu nemhuka zvichagarisana murugare nokusingaperi , uye hapana chinhu chichazvityisa .
Uye hakuzati kuchizovazve nezvirwere nokudaro hapana dikanwo yokunzvera mhuka .
Utsinye huchava chinhu chakapfuura . — Isaya 25 : 8 ; 33 : 24 ; 65 : 25 ; Mateo 6 : 9 , 10 .
‘ Anoziva Mhinduro Dzose dzeBhaibheri ’
Paimwe nguva yakapfuura mumwe mukadzi womuNew York State akatumira aichimbova mufundi biyake , airera mhuri , kopi yebhuku rinonzi Bhuku Rangu Renhau dzeBhaibheri .
Pashure penguva yakati kuti mukadziyo akagamuchira tsamba inobva kwaari umo iye akanyora pamusoro pomwanasikana wake Elizabeth :
“ Anoda bhuku chaizvo — ndiro bedzi raanoda kuti ndimuravire usiku .
Anowana nhau shanu ( nokuti iye ava namakore mashanu ) usiku , uye vhiki rakapera mudzidzisi wake weSandesikuru akandiudza kuti anogarovimba naElizabeth pakuziva mhinduro dzose dzemibvunzo yeBhaibheri .
Naizvozvo rinofanira kuve rakanyorwa nomumwe munhu anosanonzwisisa zvinodiwa navana . ”
Mudzimai weNew York anotaura pamusoro peshamwari yake , kuti : “ Ikoku kwakanga kuri kuita kwake kwokutendeseka , sezvaanonanga zvikuru uye haati aizorumbidza bhukuro kudai akanga asingaridi . ”
Tinorangarira kuti newewo uchakoshesa ichi chinyorwa chine mifananidzo yakaisvonaka , chamabhii makuru .
Nhau dzacho dzeBhaibheri dzine 116 dzinopa muravi pfungwa yeizvo Bhaibheri rinoreva nezvazvo .
Idzi nhau dzinooneka munhevedzano makaitikira zvinotika munhau .
Uchawana ichochi kuva chinobetsera zvomenemene kudzidza apo , muwirirano nezvimwe zvinoitika , zvinhu zvakaitika munhau .
Gamuchira iri bhuku rinokosha ramapeji 256 kupfurikidza nokuzadza ndokutumira kuponi .


Mibvunzo Inoda Kupindurwa
PANE imwe nguva muupenyu hwako , ungave wakabvunza , kuti : ‘ Kana Mwari ariko , neiko akabvumidza kutambura kwakawanda kudai ?
Uye neiko akakubvumidza kwenguva refu yakadai , munhau yose yomunhu ?
Ko kutambura kuchazomboguma here ? ’
Nemhaka yokusava nemhinduro dzinogutsa dzemibvunzo yakadai , vazhinji vakashatiriswa .
Vamwe vakatotsauka pakudavira muna Mwari , kana kuti vanomushora nokuda kworushambwa rwavo .
Somuenzaniso , munhu akapukunyuka Kuparadza chose chose , kupondwa kwamamirioni kwakaitwa navaNazi muHondo yeNyika II , akashatiriswa zvikuru zvokuti akataura kuti : “ Kana ukananzva mwoyo wangu , iwo uchakuchetura . ”
Mumwe murume akatambura somuuyo wechitambudzo chedzinza , icho chakaparira rufu rweshamwari nemitezo yemhuri muHondo yeNyika I , akazivisa nomutoo wokushatiriswa , kuti : “ Ko Mwari akanga ari kupiko pataimuda ? ”
Nokudaro , vanhu vazhinji vari kunetseka .
Mumurangariro wavo , kunoratidzika kuva kusingawirirani kuti Mwari worunako norudo abvumire zvinhu zvakashata kuti zviitike kwenguva refu yakadai .
Izvo Vanhu Vakaita
Ndokwechokwadi chaizvo kuti vanhu vakaita zvakashata zvikurusa mukurwisana navamwe kuburukira kumazana amakore — kureva idika , kwezviuru zvamakore .
Kukura nokutyisa kweizvi zvose kunovhiringidza ndangariro .
Pepuko zvayakaenderera mberi sezvinobvumwa , vanhu vakaita zvombo zvinoramba zvichityisa zvikuru zvokuparadza kana kuti kuremadza vamwe : pfuti hurusa , pfuti dzinomwaya mabara , ndege dzehondo , matangi ehondo , zvitsika , zvipfura marimi omwoto , zvombo zvoutachiona nenyukireya .
Somuuyo , muzana rino ramakore roga bedzi , hondo dzamarudzi dzakauraya vanenge vanhu vana mamirioni ane zana rimwe !
Mamwe mazana amamirioni akakuvadzwa kana kuti akatambura mudzimwe nzira .
Uye huzhinji hwezvinhu hwakaparadzwa , zvakadai semisha nepfuma , hahufungidziriki .
Funga nezvorusuruvaro rukurusa , kurwadziwa , uye misodzi izvo hondo yakaparira !
Kazhinji kazhinji zvikurusa ndivo vanhu vasina mhaka vakatambura : vakweguru nechembere , vana , vacheche .
Uye kazhinji kazhinji zvikurusa , vazhinji vakaita zvakashata havana kudanirwa kuzozvidavirira .
Munyika yose , kutambura kunopfuurira kusvikira zvino .
Zuva riri rose , vanhu vari kupondwa kana kuti neimwe nzira vanoitwa vanyajambwa noutsotsi .
Vanokuvadzwa kana kuti vanofira mutsaona , kubatanidza ne‘zviito zvomusikirwo ’ zvakadai semadutu ane simba , mafashamo , uye kudengenyeka kwapasi .
Vanotambura kusaruramisira , fungira mano yakaipa , urombo , nzara , kana kuti hosha , kana kuti mune dzimwe nzira dzakawanda .
Ko Mwari aigona sei kuve akasika chimwe chinhu — rudzi rwomunhu — rwatambura zvikurusa kwazvo , kazhinji kazhinji zvikuru , zana ramakore nezana ramakore ?
Chinetso Chiri Mumuviri Womunhu
Ichi chinetso chinoonwa kunyange mumuviri womunhu .
Vezvesayenzi navamwe vakaunzvera vanobvuma kuti muviri womunhu wakaitwa nomutoo unoshamisa , wakaisvonaka .
Rangarira mashomanene bedzi amativi awo anoshamisa : ziso risingadaviriki romunhu , iro risina kamera inogona kuritevedzera ; uropi hunoshamisa , uhwo hunoita kuti komupiyuta yemberi - mberi zvikurusa iratidzike kuva chinhu chisiri chounyanzvi ; mashandire pamwe anoita mativi madukusa omuviri pasina nhamburiko yedu yokuitira hanya ; nenji rokubereka , kubereka mwana akaisvonaka — mufananidzo wavabereki vake — mumwedzi mipfumbamwe bedzi .
Vanhu vazhinji vanotaura kuti ichi chinhu chounyanzvi cherongedzero , muviri womunhu , waitofanira kuve wakasikwa noMurongedzeri ano unyanzvi — Musiki , Mwari Wamasimba ose .
Asika , nomutoo unosuruvarisa , muviri mumwe chetewo unoshamisa unopera simba .
Mukufambira mberi kwenguva unokurirwa nechirwere , ukweguru , uye rufu .
Pakupedzisira unomwekesheka kuva guruva .
Haiwa kunonzwisa tsitsi sei !
Apo bedzi munhu anofanira kubetserekana namakumi amakore oruzivo rwokuzviwanira ndokuva akachenjera zvikuru , muviri unozhokoteka .
Haiwa musiano unosuruvarisa zvakadini , pamugumo wawo , utano , simba , uye runako izvo muviri wakanga une simba nokuda kwazvo pamavambo awo !
Neiko Musiki ane rudo aizoita chimwe chinhu chakaisvonaka somuviri womunhu , kuti chigoguma bedzi nomutoo unosuruvarisa zvikuru kudai ?
Neiko aizosika muviri unovamba zvakaisvonaka , une simba zvikurusa , asi unoguma nomutoo wakashata zvikuru kudai ?
Matsanangurire Anokuita Vamwe
Vamwe vakataura kuti uipi nokutambura midziyo yaMwari yokuvandudza vara redu kupfurikidza nenhamo .
Mufundisi weMethodist akabvuma , kuti : “ Kuripirwa kwezvakanaka nokuda kwezvakashata rutivi rwerongedzero yaMwari yoruponeso . ”
Akaita ikoko kuvaka vara ndokuponeswa , vanhu vakanaka vanofanira kutambura nezviito zvavanhu vakashata sorutivi rwerongedzero yaMwari .
Asika baba vano rudo vohunhu vaizoedza kuvandudza vara ravana vavo kupfurikidza nokurongedzera kuvaita kuti vaitwe vanyajambwa kupfurikidza netsotsi roupengo here ?
Rangarirawo , kuti vechiduku vazhinji vanourawa mutsaona kana kuti vanopondwa kana kuti vanofira muhondo .
Vanyajambwa vechiduku ivavo havasati vangavazve nebanza rokuvandudza vara ravo nokuti vangave vafa .
Naizvozvo pfungwa yokuti kutambura kunobvumirwa nokuda kwokuvandudza vara haisati ichiita mufungo chaizvoizvo .
Hakuna baba ano mufungo naano rudo angada kuti kutambura kana kuti ngwavaira zviwire pavadikanwi vake .
Kureva idi , baba angarongedzerera vadikanwi vake kuti vatambure nokuda kwoku‘vaka vara ’ angarangarirwa kuva asingakodzeri , kunyange anopenga .
Ipapoka nomutoo uno mufungo kungataurwa here kuti Mwari , Baba vakuru vano rudo , Musiki wokuchenjera kwose wechisiko chapose pose , noune angarongedzera kutambura sorutivi rwe‘rongedzero [ yavo ] nokuda kworuponeso ’ here ?
Ikoko kungava kubatanidza utsinye hwokunyanyisa nevara rinotyisa kwaari , vara iro isu tose tinowana risingagamuchiriki kunyange muvanhu vakaderera .
Kuwana Mhinduro
Ndokupiko kwatingatendeukira nokuda kwemhinduro dzemibvunzo yakapoteredza kubvumidza kwaMwari kutambura nouipi ?
Mibvunzo yacho zvainobatanidza Mwari , kuno mufungo kuona icho iye amene anogovera munzira yemhinduro .
Tinowana sei mhinduro dzake ?
Kupfurikidza nokuenda kumanyuko ayo Mwari anotaura kuti akanyora senhungamiro nokuda kwavanhu — Bhaibheri Dzvene , Magwaro Anoyera .
Pasinei hapo neizvo munhu angafunga pamusoro pamanyuko iwawo , akakodzerwa nokunzverwa , nokuti , sokutaura kwakaita muapostora Pauro , kuti : “ Rugwaro rwose rwakafuridzirwa naMwari uye runobetsera . . . nokuda kwokururamisa zvinhu . ”
Akanyorawo , kuti : “ Apo imi makagamuchira shoko raMwari , iro makanzwa kwatiri , imi makarigamuchira , kwete seshoko ravanhu , asi , sezvariri chaizvoizvo rezvokwadi , seshoko raMwari . ”
* — 1 VaTesaronika 2 : 13 , NW .
Kuwana mhinduro dzemibvunzo pamusoro pokubvumidzwa kwokutambura kunopfuura basa roungwaruwo zvaro .
Mhinduro dzinoisvokosha kukunzwisisa kwedu zviri kuitika iko zvino panyika , zvichaitika munguva yemberi iri pedyo , uye kuti mumwe nomumwe wedu anotapurwa sei .
Mutoro uri kwatiri timene kurega Bhaibheri , kurukurirano yaMwari nemhuri yavanhu , richitaura iro rimene .
Chii , ipapoka , charinotaura pamusoro pokuti kutambura kwakavamba sei uye nei Mwari achikubvumidza ?
Chinhu chikurusa chokunzwisisa mhinduro chine chokuita namaitirwe atakaitwa mundangariro nomupfungwa .
Bhaibheri rinoratidzira kuti Musiki akaisa mumuumbirwe wedu savanhu iri vara rinoisvokosha : chishuvo chorusununguko .
Ngatirangarirei nokupfupikisa chinobatanidzwa chaizvoizvo muchisarudzo chokuita zvaunoda nokuda kwavanhu uye kuti ikoku kune chokuita sei pakubvumidza kwaMwari kutambura .
