Chikonzero Nei Mwari Akabvumidza Kutambura
“ Hakusati kuri kwomunhu ari kufamba kururamisa nhano kunyange yake .
Ndiruramisei , Haiwa Jehovha . ” — Jeremia 10 : 23 , 24 , NW .
MASHOKO iwawo akanyorwa zviuru zvamakore pashure pokunge vanhu vasikwa .
Jeremia akaziva kuti kusvikira kuzuva rake , nhau yomunhu yakanga iri ngwavaira mukuenzanisirwa namavambo akanaka ayo Mwari akapa vabereki vedu vokutanga .
Kutaura kwaJeremia kwakasimbiswa nechinyorwa chaanopfuura makore ewedzero ane 2 500 enhau chifo chenguva yake .
Ngwavaira yavanhu yakatoipisisa .
Chii chakaipa ?
Kushandiswa Zvisinokufanira Kwechisarudzo Chokuita Zvaunoda
Vabereki vedu vokutanga havana kuona idi rokuti ivo havana kusikirwa kuti vabudirire kunze kwaMwari nemitemo yake .
Vakasarudza kuva vanozvimirira kunze kwaMwari , vachifunga havo kuti ikoko kwaizovandudza upenyu hwavo .
Asi ikoku kwakanga kuri kushandiswa zvisinokufanira kworusununguko rwavo .
Vakadarika ganhuriro dzakagadzwa dzaMwari dzechisarudzo chokuita zvaunoda . — Genesi , ganhuro 3 .
Neiko Mwari asina kungoparadza bedzi Adhama naEvha ndokutangazve navamwe vaviri vohunhu ?
Nemhaka yokuti uchangamire hwake hwapose pose namabatire ake ushe zvakanga zvapanikirwa .
Kuva kwake Mwari Wamasimba ose uye Musiki wezvisikwa zvose kunomupa maruramiro okubata ushe pavari .
Sezvo iye ari Nyakuchenjera Kwose , ubati ushe hwake hwakanakisisa nokuda kwezvisikwa zvose .
Asi kubata ushe kwaMwari zvino kwakadenhwa .
Vanhu vaigona kuita zviri nani zvikuru here panokuva vanobatwa ushe naMwari ?
Musiki aiziva zvapachokwadi mhinduro yomubvunzo iwoyo .
Nzira yechokwadi yokuti vanhu vawane yakanga iri yokuvabvumira rusununguko rusina kuganhurirwa rwavaishuva .
Naizvozvo , chikonzero chimwe , pakati pezvimwe , nei Mwari akabvumidza uipi nokutambura ndechokuratidzira nomutoo usingatongopanikirwi kana ubati ushe hwokuzvimirira hwomunhu kunze kwake huchigona kubudirira .
