Adhama naEvha vakazviunzira vamene kutambura pavari napavana vavo .
Ivo vaka‘cheka izvo ivo vakadyara . ’
“ Ivo vamene vakaita nomutoo unokuvadza ; ivo havasati vari vana [ vaMwari ] , hurema ndohwavo vamene . ” — Dheuteronomio 32 : 5 , NW .
Vabereki vedu vokutanga vakanga vanyeverwa kuti kuzvimirira kunze kwoubati ushe hwaMwari kwaizoparira rufu rwavo .
Ikoko kwakabvumikisa kuva zvokwadi .
Kupfurikidza nokusiya Mwari , ivo vakasiya manyuko avo outano noupenyu .
Vakakwegura kutozosvikira rufu rwavakurira . — Genesi 3 : 19 .
Pashure pacho , Mwari akabvumidza nguva yakakwana yokuti mhuri yomunhu iratidzire zvizere kana tsika ipi neipi yezvamatongerwe enyika , yokugarisana kwavanhu , kana kuti yomugariro wepfuma yavaiita kunze kwoubati ushe hwake yaizobvumikisa kuva inogutsa zvizere .
Ko ipi neipi yeidzi tsika yaizounza nyika inofadza , ine rugare isitongorina utsotsi kana kuti hondo here ?
Ko ipi neipi yaizokudziridza rubudiriro rwezvinhu zvokunyama nokuda kwavose here ?
Ko ipi neipi yaizokurira chirwere , ukweguru , uye rufu here ?
Ubati ushe hwaMwari hwakanga hwarongedzererwa kuita zvinhu zvose izvozvo . — Genesi 1 : 26 - 31 .
Icho Kupfuura Kwenguva Kunodzidzisa
Nokukurumidza nhau yakajekesa zvokwadi yaVaRoma 5 : 12 ( NW ) , kuti : “ Rufu rwakapararira kuvanhu vose . ”
Iyi ndima inotsanangura kuti “ chivi chakapinda munyika kupfurikidza nomunhu mumwe uye rufu kupfurikidza nechivi . ”
Apo vabereki vedu vokutanga vakapandukira ubati ushe hwaMwari , vakava vakaremara , vasina kukwana .
Uhu urema ndihwo bedzi hwavaigona kupfuudzira kuvana vavo .
Somuuyo , tose zvedu takaberekwa takaremara , takarerekera kuchirwere uye rufu .
Kupfuura kwenguva kwakazivisawo kuti vanhu vazerwe nezvivi zvikurusa vanozvibata sei kuno mumwe nomumwe .
Kwave kune hondo dzinotyisa dzakanyanyowandisa zvokusagona kudziverenga , mbengo dzedzinza norudzidziso , bvunzurudzo , utsotsi hunotyisa hwamarudzi ose , uye zviito zvoudyire namakaro .
Mukuwedzera , urombo nenzara zvakarwadza mamirioni asingaverengeki avanhu .
Mukati mezviuru zvakapfuura zvamakore , rudzi rwomunhu rwaedza rudzi rwuri rwose rwunofungidzirika rwehurumende .
Bva , rumwe norumwe rwakakundikana kugutsa zvinodikanwa zvomunhu .
Pamisi ichangobva kupfuura iyi , hurumende dzechiKomonisiti dzakarambwa munyika zhinji .
Mumarudzi ehurumende dzokusarudza kwavazhinji mune kupararirawo kwoutsotsi , urombo , kusatsiga kwomugariro wepfuma , uye ushati .
Zvamazvirokwazvo , zvimiro zvose zvehurumende yohunhu zvabvumikisa kuva zvisina kukwana .
Kupfuurirazve , Mwari akabvumira nguva kuti vanhu vasvike paukwiriri hwavo hwapamusoro hwechinowamwa chesayenzi nechezvinhu zvokunyama .
Asika ienderero mberi chaiyoiyo here apo uta nomuseve zvakatsiviwa nezvitsika zvenyukireya ?
apo vanhu vanogona kupinda muchadenga asi vasingagoni kugara pamwe chete murugare pasi pano ?
apo mamirioni avanhu anotya kubuda kunze usiku nokuda kwoutsotsi ?
Icho muedzo wenguva unoratidzira ndechokuti hakubviri zvikuru kuti vanhu va‘tungamirire nhano dzavo vamene ’ nomutoo unobudirira kupinda zvakuri kwavari kurarama vasina zvokudya , mvura , uye mhepo .
Takasikirwa kuva vanotsamira panhungamiro yoMuiti wedu sokungosikwa kwatakaitwa kuti titsamire pane zvokudya , mvura , uye mhepo . — Mateo 4 : 4 .
Kupfurikidza nokubvumidza uipi nokutambura , Mwari akaratidzira kwechigarire miuyo inosuruvarisa yokushandisa zvisina kufanira chisarudzo chokuita zvaunoda .
Ichi chipo chinokosha zvokuti panokutorera vanhu chisarudzo chokuita zvavanoda , Mwari akavabvumira kuona icho kushandiswa zvisina kufanira kwacho kunoreva .
Pamusoro pechisarudzo chokuita zvaunoda , chinyorwa chinonzi “ Statement of Principles of Conservative Judaism ” chinoti : “ Kana pasina bviro chaiyo yavanhu yokuita chisarudzo chakaipa pakunangana nechakanaka nechakashata , mufungo wose wechisarudzo hauna revo . . . .
Huzhinji hwokutambura kwenyika nomutoo wakananga hunoparirwa nokushandisa zvisina kufanira kwedu chisarudzo chokuita zvaunoda chatakapiwa . ”
Zvechokwadi , Jeremia akanga akarurama paakati : “ Hakusati kuri kwomunhu anofamba kururamisa kunyange nhano yake . ”
Uyewo Soromoni akanga akaruramawo paakati : “ Munhu akadzora munhu kusvikira pakuvadziko yake . ” — Muparidzi 8 : 9 , NW .
Nomutoo wakasimba , ikoko kunoratidzira kusakwanisa kwomunhu kubvisa kutambura .
Kunyange Soromoni , nouchenjeri hwake hwose , pfuma , uye simba haati aigona kururamisa nhamo inobva muubati ushe hwohunhu .
Ko , ipapoka , Mwari achagumisa here kutambura ?
Achazombotusa vanhu nokuda kwokutambura kwavo kwakapfuura here ?
