Nyika Itsva Isitongorina Kutambura
“ Zvinhu zvekare hazvisati zvichizorangarirwa , uyewo hazvisati zvichizofungwa mumwoyo .
Asi farai , imi vanhu , uye farisisai nokusingaperi mune zvandiri kusika . ” — Isaya 65 : 17 , 18 , NW .
MASHOKO iwawo ouporofita akafuridzirwa naMwari anopfuura makore 2 700 akapfuura .
Anorondedzera , muchikamu , icho upenyu huchava hwakaita munguva yemberi .
Rini ?
Pashure pokunge Mwari agumisa tsika ino yezvinhu .
Uporofita huzhinji hweBhaibheri hunojekesa kuti idonzo raMwari rokubvisa tsika ino yezvinhu nokukurumidza uye kuitsiva nenyika itsva isitongorina kutambura kupi nokupi .
Haiwa upenyu huchava hwakasiana sei munyika itsva iyeyo mukuenzanisirwa noupenyu munhau yose yekare yomunhu !
Shoko rouporofita raMwari rinotiudza kuti ichava isitongorina chose chose hondo , utsotsi , urombo , uye kusaruramisira .
Zvichapfuura nokusingaperi zvichava chirwere norufu .
Hakusati kuchizovazve nehurumende dzinokamuranisa , marudzidziso , kana gadziriro dzomugariro wepfuma dzakabvumikisa kuva dzisina kukwana zvikuru .
Misodzi yomufaro ichatsiva misodzi yorusuruvaro nokuti zvichapfuura nokusingaperi zvichava uipi nokutambura .
Zvakadeya Kufananidzirwa Muuporofita hweBhaibheri
Cherekedza kuti migariro yakadaro yakadeya kuoneswa sei mumuenzanisiro uno wouporofita hweBhaibheri :
Hakuchinazve Hondo : “ Iye anogumisa hondo kusvikira kumigume - gume yapasi . ”
“ Rudzi harusati ruchizosimudzira munondo mukurwisana norudzi , uyewo iwo haasati vachizodzidzirazve hondo . ” — Isaya 2 : 4 , NW .
Ruramisiro Nokuda Kwomunhu Ari Wose : “ Ndichaita ruramisiro rwonzi rwokupima narwo uye kururama mudziyo wokusandaridza nawo . ” — Isaya 28 : 17 , NW .
Kusatongova Norutyo : “ Ivo vachagara chaizvoizvo , munhu mumwe nomumwe pasi pomuzambiringa wake napasi pomuonde wake , uye hakusati kuchizova nomunhu unovatyisa . ”
“ Zvamazvirokwazvo ivo vachabvumikisa kuva paivhu ravo muchengeteko . ” — Ezekieri 34 : 27 , NW .
Nzara Inobviswa : “ Pasi pano pachava nezviyo zvizhinji ; pamusoro pamakomo pachava nezvinofashukira . ”
“ Muti womumunda unofanira kubereka zvibereko zvawo , uye nyika iyo imene ichabereka zvibereko zvayo . ” — Ezekieri 34 : 27 , NW .
Hakuchinazve Ukweguru Kana Kuti Chirwere : “ Nyama yake ngaive itsva zvikuru kupfuura yomuupwere ; ngaadzokere kumazuva esimba rake roupwere . ”
“ Hakuna mugari wemo achataura , kuti : ‘ Ndinorwara . ’ ” — Isaya 33 : 24 , NW .
Rufu , Kuchema , Uye Kurwadziwa Zvaparara Nokusingaperi : “ [ Mwari ] uchapukuta musodzi uri wose pameso avo , uye rufu haruchazovipozve , uyewo kuchema kana kurira kana kurwadziwa hazvichazovipozve . Zvinhu zvekare zvapfuura . ” — Zvakazarurwa 21 : 4 , NW .
Haitapurwi Nenguva Yakapfuura
Nyika itsva inouya yokuita kwaMwari ichava inogutsa zvikuru zvokuti kufarikanywa kwoupenyu kunoitwa navagari vapasi hakusati kuchizodziviswa , kunyange neyeuko dzipi nedzipi dzisingafadzi dzokutambura kwekare .
Mifungo mizhinji inovaka nemibato zvichava upenyu hwezuva riri rose ravanhu muzera irero idzva pashoma napashoma zvichadzima yeuko dzakashata dzakapfuura .
Chipikirwa chaMwari ndeichi : “ Zvinhu zvekare hazvisati zvichizoyeukwa , uyewo hazvisati zvichizofungwa mumwoyo . ”
Vanhu vachava vano “ fara nokusingaperi ” mune icho Mwari achaunza munyika yose .
“ Nyika yose yazozorora , yazova isitongorina vhiringidziko .
Vanhu vava vanofara nokudanidzira kwokufara . ” — Isaya 65 : 17 , 18 ; 14 : 7 , NW .
Nhasi , “ kariro inosundirwa mberi inorwarisa mwoyo , ” sokurondedzera kunoita Bhaibheri .
Asi mugariro uchashandurwa munyika itsva .
Panguva iyeyo “ chinhu chinoshuviwa [ chichava ] muti woupenyu apo iwo unouya . ”
Mwoyo haisati ichizonetswa nokutambura kana kuti nekariro dzisingazadziki .
Panzvimbo pakwo , ichazadzwa negutsikano nomufaro nokuda kwezvinhu zvizhinji zvinoshamisa izvo Mwari achagovera nokuda kwemhuri yomunhu .
Ubati Ushe Hwakasiana
Panzvimbo pokuva noubati ushe hwomunhu husingagutsi hunozvimirira kunze kwaMwari , nyika itsva ichava noubati ushe hwakasiana chose chose .
Chiremera chinodzora chichatorerwa vanhu .
Havasati vachizobvumirwazve kubata ushe vakazvimirira kunze kwaMwari .
Uporofita hweBhaibheri hunoti : “ Mumazuva amadzimambo iwawo [ vabati ushe vari musimba zvino ] Mwari wokudenga uchagadza umambo [ mudenga ] husati huchizotongoparadzwa .
Uye umambo ihwo humene hahusati huchizopfuuridzirwa kuna vamwe vanhu vapi navapi [ zvakunenge kusichinazve ubati ushe ] . Ihwo huchapwanya ndokugumisa maumambo iwawa ose [ ayo ariko zvino ] , uye ihwo humene huchagara kusvikira kunguva dzisingazivikanwi . ” — Dhanieri 2 : 44 , NW .
Jesu akadzidzisa vateveri vake kunyengeterera ubati ushe hutsva hwapasi apo iye akati : “ Umambo hwenyu ngahuuye .
Kuda kwenyu ngakuitwe , somudenga , napasi panowo . ” — Mateo 6 : 10 , NW .
Iyeyo ichava hurumende itsva yorudzi rwomunhu — ubati ushe hwokudenga hwaMwari hunodzorwa noUmambo hwake huri musimba raKristu .
Uye pasi pano , vabatiri vakavimbika vohunhu vaMwari vachatarisira zvinhu mukuwirirana nenhungamiro yaMwari .
Muapostora Petro akataura nezve iyi gadziriro itsva se “ matenga matsva nepasi idzva zvatiri kumirira mukuwirirana nechipikirwa chake , uye kururama kunogara muna izvozvi . ”
Ubati ushe ihwohwo hwoUmambo ndihwo dzidziso huru yeBhaibheri .
‘ Chisiko Chinosunungurwa ’
Uhu ubati ushe hutsva huchadzorawo chose chose masimba omusikirwo apasi .
‘ Masimba omusikirwo ’ akadai sokudengenyeka kwapasi , madutu emhepo , mafashamo , kana kuti kusanaya kwemvura hazvisati zvichizoparirazve nhamo .
Jesu iye amene akaratidzira simba rake mukuraira aya masimba .
Pane imwe nhambo , somuenzaniso , apo igwa iro Jesu navadzidzi vake vakanga vakakwira rakanga rodokubheukira mudutu guru , iye akateramisa mhepo negungwa .
Vadzidzi vashamiswa vakazivisa , kuti : “ Uyu munhu worudzii , zvokuti kunyange mhepo negungwa zvinomuteerera ? ” — Mateo 8 : 23 - 27 , NW .
Naizvozvo pasi , uyewo chisiko chohunhu , zvichawana rusununguko rwusingaenzanisirwi .
“ Chisiko icho chimene chichasunungurwa muuranda hwoushati ndokuva norusununguko rune mbiri rwavana vaMwari .
Nokuti isu tinoziva kuti chisiko chose chinoramba chichigomera pamwe chete uye chiri kurwadziwa pamwe chete kusvikira zvino . ” — VaRoma 8 : 21 , 22 , NW .
Tinogona kuva nechokwadi here chokuti ubati ushe hwohunhu nokukurumidza huchaguma uye kuti hurumende itsva yaMwari ichatora kutarisirwa kwezvinhu zvose zvapasi ?
Tinogona zvamazvirokwazvo , nokuti Changamire weChisiko Chapose pose akapa shoko rake : “ ‘ Zano rangu ndimene richagara , uye ndichaita chinhu chiri chose chandinofarira ’ ; . . . ndakatochitaura ; ndichachiunzawo .
Ndakachiumba , ndichachiitawo . ” — Isaya 46 : 10 , 11 , NW .
“ Nguva Yakagadzwa ”
Ko ikoko kuchaitika sei ?
Kuchaitika rini ?
Shoko raMwari rinoti : “ Kune nguva yakagadzwa nokuda kwechinhu chiri chose . ”
Ikoku kunobatanidza nguva yakagadzwa yokuti Mwari ati ‘ zvaringana ! ’
uye kugumisa uipi nokutambura .
Dhanieri akataura nezve “ nguva yakagadzwa yomugumo . ”
Jesu akataurawo nezve “ nguva yakagadzwa . ” — Marko 13 : 32 , 33 .
Hungu , Mwari akazvigadzira nguva chaiyoiyo yokupindira muzvinhu zvavanhu ndokubvisa chose kuedza kunosuruvarisa muubati ushe hwomunhu hwokuzvimirira kunze kwake .
“ Mwari wechokwadi achatonga vose vari vaviri vakarurama navakaipa , nokuti kune nguva yechinhu chiri chose . ”
Uye ufakazi huri mukuzadzika kwouporofita hweBhaibheri hunoratidzira kuti nguva yakagoverwa yaMwari yokubvumidza kutambura ichaguma nokukurumidza .
Apo ganhuriro yenguva iyeyo inenge yapera , iye achaparadza chose chose tsika isingagutsi youbati ushe hwohunhu iyo kwezviuru zvamakore yakaunza kutambura kukuru kumhuri yomunhu . — Mateo 24 : 3 - 14 ; 2 Timotio 3 : 1 - 5 , 13 ; Zvakazarurwa 19 : 11 - 21 .
Apo Mwari anoita marutongeso ake , cherekedza chichaitika kuna avo vanozviisa pasi poubati ushe hwake , mukusiana naavo vasingadaro : “ Muchinguvana chiduku , uye wakaipa haachazovipozve ; . . . asi vanyoro ivo vamene vachagara nhaka yapasi , uye zvamazvirokwazvo vachawana mufaro wavo mukuru mukuwanda kworugare . ”
“ Kana vari vana vavakaipa , zvamazvirokwazvo vachaparadzwa .
Vakarurama ivo vamene vachagara nhaka yapasi , uye vachagara nokusingaperi pariri . ”
“ Cherekedzai wakarurama , nokuti nguva yemberi yomunhu iyeyo ichava ine rugare .
Asi vadariki ivo vamene zvamazvirokwazvo vachaparadzwa chose chose pamwe chete . ” — Pisarema 37 : 10 , 11 , 28 , 29 , 37 , 38 ; onawo Zvirevo 2 : 21 , 22 ; Mateo 5 : 5 .
Asika zvakadiniko namabhirioni avanhu vakatofa ?
Vachabetserekana sei nenyika itsva ?
Kupfurikidza norumuko , kudzorerwa kuupenyu pasi pano chaipo .
Vachadzoka kubva mumakuva ndokupiwa banza rokufarikanya upenyu nokusingaperi .
Shoko raMwari rinosimbisira , kuti : “ Kuchava norumuko rwavose vari vaviri vakarurama navasakarurama . ”
Uye Jesu akaenzanisira ikoku kupfurikidza nokumutsa vanhu vakafa , vakadai saRazaro nomwanakomana wechirikadzi yeNaini . — Johane 11 : 38 - 44 ; Ruka 7 : 11 - 16 .
“ Tuso ”
Haiwa kunofadza sei kuziva kuti donzo raMwari nderokugumisa kutambura uye kuunza nyika itsva yakarurama !
Funga nezvokurarama mamirioni amakore — zvamazvirokwazvo , nokusingaperi — muutano hwakakwana nomufaro pakati pemhoteredzo dzeparadhiso , umo uipi nokutambura zvichava nokusingaperi zvinhu zvomunguva yakapfuura !
Hausati waizobvuma here kuti iyi “ tuso ” inoitwa naMwari kurudzi rwomunhu — munguva yose isingagumi — inopfuura makore mashomanene ane zviuru ane mwero ayo Mwari akabvumidza kutambura ?
Uyewo haisati ichipfuura zvikuru makore ane 70 kana kuti 80 okutambura here — kana kuti mashoma — atingave takatsungirira somunhu mumwe nomumwe munduramo yedu ?
Murangariro Wokuona Zviri Kure
Mumurangariro wake wokuona zvinhu zviri kure , Musiki anoziva kuti kwakanga kuchikosha kuti atange kugadzikisa nhau dzinokosha zvikuru dzamaruramiro ake okubata ushe saChangamire weChisiko Chapose pose nokururama kwoubati ushe hwake .
Uye kwakanga kuchikosha kugadzikisa nhau yokushandiswa zvakafanira uye zvisinokufanira kworusununguko rwechisarudzo .
Kwakanga kuriwo madikanwa kuratidzira kuti chisiko chake chakakwana mukuti vanhu vanoteerera mukuvimbika mitemo yake yakarurama vanogona kuchengeta perero kwaari mukutambura nomukuedzwa kunoitwa navabati ushe venyika , muenzaniso wakatanhamara waikoku uchiva Mwanakomana wake amene , Jesu , paaiveri pasi pano .
Achinge agadzikisa nhau dzose , Mwari haasati achizobvumira uipi nokutambura kuti zvivepozve kuti zvishatse nyika yose ine rugare .
“ Kutambudzika hakusati kuchizosimuka kwenguva yechipiri . ” — Nahumi 1 : 9 , NW .
Mukati menguva yose isingagumi inouya , Mwari anogona kushandisa chakaitika muzviuru izvi zvamakore akapfuura sokunge chaiva chitemeso chakaisvonaka mudare rapamusoro .
Chisarudzo charo chinogona kushandiswa panguva ipi neipi yomunguva yemberi , munzvimbo ipi neipiwo zvayo muchisiko chapose pose , kana panikiro dzichizombomukazve pamusoro pouchangamire hwaMwari kana kuti kushandiswa zvakafanira kwechisarudzo chokuita zvaunoda .
Chii Chauchasarudza ?
Nhasi tine chisarudzo .
Tinogona kushandisa chisarudzo chedu chokuita zvatinoda munzira mbiri : Tinogona kusarudza kufuratira madonzo aMwari , kugutsikana noubati ushe husina kukwana hwohunhu ndokugoverana mugumo wahwo , kana tinogona kushandisa rusununguko rwedu rwechisarudzo kudzidza icho madonzo aMwari ari uye icho tinodikanirwa kuita kuti timufadze savadzorwi vakazvipira voUmambo hwake .
Jesu mumunyengetero kuna Mwari , akati : “ Ikoku kunoreva upenyu husingaperi , kupinza kwavo zivo yenyu , Mwari wechokwadi bedzi , neyouyo wamakatuma , Jesu Kristu . ”
Naizvozvo kana tichida upenyu munyika itsva , tinodikanirwa kuita nhamburiko dzokudzidza zvokwadi pamusoro paMwari , madonzo ake , uye zvinodikanwa zvake .
Cherekedza kuti Bhaibheri rinozivisa sei , kuti : “ Jehovha anewe chero bedzi uchibvumikisa kuva naye ; uye kana uchimutsvaka , iye achazvirega achiwanwa newe , asi kana ukamusiya iye achakusiya . ” — 2 Makoronike 15 : 2 , NW .
Nguva iri kuperera nyika ino yekare ; itsva iri kuuya : “ Nyika iri kupfuura ndozviri kuitawo ruchiva rwayo , asi iye unoita kuda kwaMwari unogara nokusingaperi . ”
Ndechipiko chauchasarudza — nyika yekare iri kupfuura kana kuti itsva iri kuuya ?
Shoko raMwari rinoti : “ Ndaisa upenyu norufu pamberi pako , chikomborero nechituko ; uye unofanira kusarudza upenyu kuti ugoramba uri mupenyu , iwe navana vako , kupfurikidza nokuda Jehovha Mwari wako , kupfurikidza nokuteerera inzwi rake uye kupfurikidza nokunamatira kwaari ; nokuti iye ndiye upenyu hwako nourefu hwamazuva ako . ” — Dheuteronomio 30 : 19 , 20 .
Chishuvo chako here chokufarikanya zvikomborero izvo Mwari akachengetera avo vanotsinhiranisa kuda kwavo nokwake ?
Vabudisi vamagazini ino kana kuti Zvapupu zvaJehovha kunzvimbo ipi neipi munyika zvichafara kukubatsira , pachena , kudzidza zvakawanda pamusoro paikoku .
