MURUDZII rwenyika rwaungada kugara ?
Rudzii rwenguva yemberi rwaunoda nokuda kwavana vako ?
Kudai waigona kuva noutano hwakakwana uye usingafi , waizosarudza here ?
Ungapindura sei mibvunzo iyeyo ?
Vanhu vazhinjisa , pasinei hapo nomugariro worudzidziso kana kuti zvamatongerwe enyika , vangada kugara munyika yorugare namafashafasha .
Vangagamuchira nyika yeruramisiro yakakwana uye tsinhirano , umo mungave musina ushati ; kana kuti mungave musina mutemo mumwe nokuda kwavapfumi uye mumwe nokuda kwavarombo .
Uye nokuda kwavana vako , pasina panikiro ungada kuva nezvokudya zvakawanda , musha unofadza , uye dzidzo yakanaka .
Namamwe mashoko , ungada kusimbisira nguva yechokwadi yakatsiga nokuda kwako umene navana vako .
Uye kudai waizopiwa banza , waizosarudza kuva noutano hwakakwana uye kurarama nguva refu yakaringanira kuita zvishuvo zvako zvose zvakanaka namagwinyiro , kunyange kufarikanya upenyu husingaperi paparadhiso yapasi .
Kose ikoku hakuzati kuri fungidziro isingabviri .
Ishoko reBhaibheri iro Zvapupu zvaJehovha zviri kuparidzira mupasi rose , kubatanidza nyika dzomuMabvazuva dzeEurope .
Tariro Inoshanda yeBhaibheri Nokuda Kwenguva Yemberi
Zviporofita zvinovimbika zveBhaibheri zvakanyorwa mumazana mazhinji amakore akapfuura zvakadeya kuzivisa zvinoitika zvomuzana ramakore rechi 20 , ‘ hondo [ dzedu ] namaguhu ehondo ’ ; ‘ kudengenyeka kwapasi [ redu ] neperevedzo dzokudya munzvimbo nenzvimbo ’ ; ‘ shungu [ yedu ] yamarudzi , asati achiziva nzira yokubuda nayo , vanhu vachingunopera simba nokuda kworutyo nekariro yezvinoitika zvinowira pasi ’ ; ‘ kuparadza [ kwedu ] nokushatiswa kwapasi . ’ — Ruka 21 : 10 - 33 ; Zvakazarurwa 11 : 18 .
Bva , zvinoitika zvose izvozvi nezvimwe zvizhinji chiratidzo chechokwadi chokuti nyika itsva yakapikirwa yaMwari iriwo pedyo zvikuru .
Iyoyi inobatanidza “ matenga matsva nepasi idzva , ” ndiko kuti , ubati ushe hwenyika itsva , hurumende yokudenga , uye chaunga chapasi chakashandurwa ‘ umo kururama kunogara mazviri . ’
Kunoreva nyika itsva umo ‘ marwadzo , rufu , uye kuchema zvisati zvichizovamozve . ’ — Isaya 65 : 17 - 25 ; 2 Petro 3 : 13 ; Zvakazarurwa 21 : 1 - 4 .
Sezvinooneka , hapana sangano rezvamatongerwe enyika , pasinei hapo nokuti nderapachokwadi sei uye rinoitira hanya , rinokwanisa kuita purogiramu yakadaro .
Changamire Ishe bedzi wechisiko chapose pose , Jehovha Mwari , ane zvose zviri zviviri chido nesimba rokuita ikoku .
Nokuda kwechikonzero ichecho Mwanakomana wake , Kristu Jesu , akadzidzisa vateveri vake kunyengetera , kuti : “ Baba vedu vari mumatenga , zita renyu ngaritsveneswe .
Umambo hwenyu ngahuuye .
Kuda kwenyu ngakuitike , somudenga , uyewo pamusoro papasi . ” — Mateo 6 : 9 , 10 , NW .
Kuda kwaMwari ndekwokuti pasi rinofanira kuva imbwe rinokosha rinon’animira muchisiko chapose pose , rigarwe nemhuri yavanhu ino rudo norugare .
Nokukurumidza Mwari achaita chiito chokuunza iyeyo .
Chichava chiito chokuchenura kubvisa papasi shatiso yose navashatisi .
Shatiso yose , ingava yokunyama kana kuti yetsika , ichabviswa papasi .
Ndianiko achasara ?
Jesu akati : “ Vanofara ndivo vanyoro , nokuti vachagara nhaka pasi . ” — Mateo 5 : 5 ; Zvakazarurwa 16 : 14 - 16 .
Unoda here kuva pakati paavo vanyoro vachava nechikomborero chaMwari ?
Ipapo onana neZvapupu zvaJehovha munzvimbo yawakavakidzana nayo uye kumbira fundo yeBhaibheri yapamusha yapachena , pasina kuva nomusengwa .
Zvibvumikisire umene chiri “ kuda kwaMwari kwakanaka , kunogamuchirika uye kwakakwana . ”
Uye ipapo ndokukuita . — VaRoma 12 : 2 .
