Zvakadiniko Nenguva Yemberi ?
Neiko rugare pakati pomunhu nemhuka ruchifadza zvikuru kwazvo ?
Imhaka yokuti vanhu pakuvamba vakasikwa kuti vave norugare nemhuka , kunyange dziya dzinorongwa muboka sedzinorura .
Apo Mwari akaita murume nomukadzi vokutanga , akavaisa munharaunda yeparadhiso yapasi kuti vafarikanye upenyu .
Rakanga riri donzo rake kuti ivo vave navana ndokufutunura miganhu yeParadhiso irero rapakuvamba kutozosvikira ramonzvera pasi rose .
Munzvimbo iyeyo yose , rudzi rwomunhu rwaizodzora mhuka murugare .
Nhauro yaGenesi inoti : “ Ngavadzore hove dzomugungwa nezvisikwa zvinobhururuka zvomumatenga uye mhuka dzinopfuyiwa nepasi rose uye mhuka iri yose inofamba papasi . . . .
Pashure paikoko Mwari akaona chinhu chiri chose chaakanga aita uye , tarira ! chakanga chakanaka zvikuru . ” — Genesi 1 : 26 - 31 ; 2 : 9 , NW .
Uku kudzorwa kwemhuka kwakanga kusati kuchizoitwa noutsinye .
Vanhu nemhuka vakaitirwa kugara pamwe chete murugare .
Ikoku kunogona kuonwa muidi rokuti apo mhuka dzaipfuura pamberi pomunhu aidzitumidza mazita , akanga asina kushongedzera zvombo .
Uye kwakanga kusina kududzwa kworutyo rwairatidzirwa nomunhu kana kuti zvimwe nemhuka . — Genesi 2 : 19 , 20 .
Donzo Rapakuvamba Richazadzika
Nomufaro , donzo riye rapakuvamba raMwari richaitwa nokukurumidza , apo hurumende dzose dzakaitwa nomunhu dzinenge dzatsiviwa noUmambo hwaMwari , uhwo hunobata ushe huri kudenga .
Ubati ushe hwaMwari zvahunenge hwagadzikiswazve chose chose pamusoro papasi rose , donzo rapakuvamba raMwari nokuda kwapasi navagari varo vohunhu uye mhuka richapfuurira kuzadzika .
Miuyo inochinja youbati ushe hwaMwari inosanorondedzerwa muuporofita huzhinji hweBhaibheri .
Somuenzaniso , cherekedza izvo Isaya akanyora mufuridzirwo , zvinoti : “ Bere richagara zvamazvirokwazvo kwechinguvana negwaianarume , uye ingwe iyo imene ichavata pasi pamwe chete nembudzana , uye mhuru neshumba duku yava nezenze nemhuka inosanodyiswa pamwe chete ; uye kakomanawo zvako kachava mutungamiriri pazviri . Uye mombe nebere izvo zvimene zvichadya ; zvichavata pasi pamwe chete nemhuru .
Uye kunyange shumba ichadya uswa kungofanana nemukono . Hazvisati zvichizoita kuvadziko ipi neipi kana kuti kuparira ruparadziko rupi norupi mugomo rangu rose dzvene ; nokuti pasi zvirokwazvo richazara nezivo yaJehovha sokufukidza kunoita mvura gungwa rimene . ” — Isaya 11 : 6 , 7 , 9 , NW .
Humwe uporofita hunoratidzawo rugare rukurusa ruchavamo munyika itsva yaMwari .
Muna ikoku Mika akadeya kuzivisa , kuti : “ Ivo vachatofanira kupfura minondo yavo kuva miromo yamapadza namapfumo avo kuva zvisanzauriso .
Ivo havasati vachizosimudzirana munondo , rudzi ruchimukirana norudzi , uyewo ivo havasati vachizodzidzirazve hondo .
Uye ivo vachagara zvomenemene , munhu mumwe nomumwe pasi pomuzambiringa wake napasi pomuonde wake , uye hakusati kuchizova nomunhu anovadederesa . ” — Mika 4 : 3 , 4 , NW .
Hakuna neimwe yezvikara panguva iyeyo zvichakangaidza rugare rworudzi rwomunhu , nokuti shoko rouporofita raMwari rinoti : “ Ndichaita navo sungano yorugare , uye zvirokwazvo ndichasakisa kuti mhuka inokuvadza ipere panyika , uye zvomenemene vachagara murenje muchengeteko ndokurara mumasango . . . .
Uye vachabvumikisa zvomenemene kuva paivhu ravo muchengeteko . ” — Ezekieri 34 : 25 , 27 , NW .
Naizvozvo rugare netsinhirano muParadhiso iyeyo yose yakadzorerwa zvichava zvakakwana .
Ndicho chikonzero nei migariro imomo ingagona kurondedzerwa mubhuku rokupedzisira reBhaibheri neiyi nzira , kuti : “ ‘ [ Mwari ] achapukuta musodzi uri wose pameso avo , uye rufu haruchazovipozve , uye kuchema kana kuti kurira kana kuti kurwadziwa hazvichazovipozve .
Zvinhu zvekare zvapfuura . ’ Uye Uyo agere pachigaro choumambo akati : ‘ Tarirai !
Ini ndiri kuita kuti zvinhu zvose zvive zvitsva . ’
Uyewo , iye anoti : ‘ Nyora , nokuti mashoko aya akatendeka uye ndeechokwadi . ’ ” — Zvakazarurwa 21 : 4 , 5 , NW .
Hungu , akatendeka uye ndeechokwadi .
Ikoku kunoreva kuti tinogona kuvimba nezvipikirwa zvaMwari , nokuti mukusafanana navanhu vasina kukwana , iye ane simba , uchenjeri , noutsungi hwokuita madonzo ake .
Sokutaura kwakaita mumwe wavabatiri vakatendeka vaMwari munguva dzekare : “ Hakuna nerimwe ramashoko ose akanaka ayo Jehovha Mwari wako akataura kwauri rakakundikana .
Iwo ose akazadzika kwauri . Hakuna shoko rimwe rawo rakakundikana . ” — Joshua 23 : 14 , NW ; onawo Isaya 55 : 11 .
Tinogona kuva nechivimbo chimwe chetecho chokuti nokukurumidza , munyika itsva yaMwari , donzo rake rapakuvamba nokuda kwepasi rino , nokuda kwavanhu , uye nokuda kwemhuka richazadzika .
Rugare runopiwa naMwari ruchava chinhu chaichoicho mupasi rose .
Uye rugare rwakadaro harusati ruchizobata ushe bedzi pakati pavanhu asi ruchavawo runoratidzirwa munzvimbo yemhuka .
Vechiduku Vanobvunza Kuti . . .
Ndinogona Sei Kuita Kuti Mukomana Arege Kundinetsa ?
David mukomana anoisvodiwa zvikuru muchikoro .
Uye nokukurumidza , mugodo romusikana ari wose muchikoro , akava anokufarira !
Iye akakukumbira kanoverengeka kuti uvhakache naye , uye nguva iri yose iwe wakaramba .
Asi David anokuudza kuti hakuna mumwe musikana akambomuita kuti anzwe nenzira iyeyo uye kuti iye haangagamuchiri aiwa nokuda kwemhinduro .
Iwe haudi kukuvadza kunzwa kwake , asi sezvingabvira unoziva icho iye anorangarira .
Neiko iye asingaregi bedzi kukunetsa ?
MHANDARA kunzvimbo iri yose ( uye kazhinji kazhinji majaya nhasi ) vari kudenhwa navavanofunda navo uye vavanoshanda navo vanovapa ngwariro yorudo isingadiwi .
Kazhinji kazhinji kupfimba kunoguma nekokero yakajeka yokupinda muutere hwevatano .
Waizoita sei kudai ikoko kwaizoitika kwauri ?
Nyaya iri muPsychology Today , inoti : “ Kana murume achikarakadzira vatano , kupfurikidza nokutaura kwezevezeve kana kuti nechiratidzo chomuviri , unofanira kudavidza nokukurumidza .
Kana ukarega , kunyarara kwako kunomukurudzira kupfuurira . ”
Naizvozvo unofanira kuita chimwe chinhu — asika chiiko ?
Chikonzero Nei Kuramba Kwakaoma
Imwe mhandara inonzi Sherron inobvuma nomutoo wakajeka zvikuru , kuti : “ Kazhinji kazhinji hakuna kuoma kuramba kana mukomana akashata . ”
Chinetso ndechokuti , isu tose tinoda kupiwa ngwariro .
Uye apo inenge ichibva kune mumwe munhu watinoyemura kana kuti watinowana achikwezva , hakusati kuri nyore kuiramba .
Asika zvibvunze umene , kuti : ‘ Munhu uyu ane nharidzano dzangu here , murangariro wangu womudzimu , tsika dzangu ? ’
Kana kusina kudaro , kudavidza kuzvikarakadziro zvake kungasanokuisa panzira inoenda kungwavaira .
Kunyanguvezvo , ungananganawo nedzvinyiriro ine simba yavezera rako yokuti urwisane nemipimo yako yorudzidziso .
Dana muduku anoshuma , kuti : “ Vasikana vokubasa vanondigombedzera kuti ndindodzana navo ; vanobvunza chikonzero nei ndisiri kuronga kuvhakacha noupi noupi . ”
Kana uchiri muchikoro , vaunofunda navo nomutoo wakafanana vangakukurudzira kuti uvhakache navamwe vavakomana ikoko .
Urwu rudzi rwedzvinyiriro runogona kunetesa zviri nyore ushingi hwako .
Chii chaungaita kuti uhusimbise ?
Gadza Miganhu
Chirevo chekare chinoti , “ Kudzivirira kukuvara kunokosha kupfuura kurapa . ”
Maria anobvuma .
Anoti : “ Ndinoita kuti kuzivikanwe kuti ini ndiri mumwe weZvapupu zvaJehovha . ”
Apo vakomana vanoziva kuti une mipimo yakakwirira yetsika , sezvingabvira vangakunetsa zvishoma .
Shambidziko yakafanira inoitawo rutivi runokosha mukusakurudzira ngwariro isingadiwi .
Mumwe mutarisiri weNew York akaziva ikoku apo iye akavamba kuva nezvinetso navarume kunzvimbo yake yebasa .
Iye anoti : “ Kunyange zvazvo ndakanga ndichibishaira pabasa rangu , handina kuitarira .
Naizvozvo ndakasunga bvudzi rangu uye ndakatanga kupfeka hembe dzeshinda namagogorozi uye zvipfeko zvinosonwa mumisha pakuenda kubasa .
Ndairatidzika ndichibishaira , kwakafanana nokuti ndiripo kuti ndishande , kwete kuzotamba zvorudo . ”
Chokwadika , chitarisiko chakadaro chingava chisiri madikanwa nokuda kwomugariro wako , asi chinoenzanisira chaizvo dikanwo yokuva nechokwadi chokuti mupfekero wako nokushambidzika zvinopa kuorora kwakafanira . — 1 Timotio 2 : 9 .
Kusarudza kwako shamwari ndichimwe chitemeso chinokosha .
Bhaibheri rinoti : “ Iye anofamba navanhu vakachenjera achava akachenjera , asi iye ari kuva nokubata namapenzi [ mutsika ] achaguma nomutoo wakashata . ”
Naizvozvo rega kusonganirana — kana kuti kunyange kuteerera — vanhu vanotaura misere yakashata kana kuti vanoganza nokuzvipinza muvatano .
Kana ukadaro , vamwe vangawana mufungo usina kururama pamusoro pako .
Erica muduku anotaura kuti apo kutaura kusingachadzoreki , iye anovaudza kuti , “ Ichecho chiratidzo changu chokuti ndiende , ” uye ivo vanowana pfundo racho .
Kuva “ Rusvingo ”
Kunyange zvakadaro , padzimwe nguva kunyange kusimbisa kuti iwe uri muKristu hakuna kukwana kuti uodze mwoyo vamwe vakomana .
( “ Kunoita musiano wei kuti iwe uri muKristu ? ” rimwe jaya rakatsunga rakarangarira kudaro .
“ Unongova hako mukadzi , uye ini ndinongova hangu murume . ” )
Unobata sei mugariro wakadaro ?
Eya , rangarira muenzaniso weBhaibheri womusikana weShuramiti .
Akapfimbwa nomumwe wavarume vakapfuma zvikuru , vakaisvochenjera , uye vane simba zvikurusa vakambova papasi — Mambo Soromoni .
Zvisinei , iye akanga achitodanana nomufudzi anozvininipisa wokumusha kwake .
Naizvozvo aigona sei kuita kuti Soromoni arege kumunetsa ?
Pakutanga , akanga achizvirangarira amene nomutoo wakafanira .
Akati : “ Ndinongovawo zvangu ruva romubani ramahombekombe egungwa . ”
Kuva nechimiro chokuzvininipisa chimwe chetecho kunokosha nokuti mudziyo wokutanga uyo vanyengeri vanoshandisa ndiko kutaura kwokunyengera .
MuShuramiti akanga ari munyoro zvokusagona kuva nyajambwa wakwo .
Uye apo “ vakunda veJerusarema ” vakashandisa dzvinyiriro yavezera rimwe chetero yokuedza kumugombedzera kubvuma Soromoni , akaita kuti vapike ‘ kusamutsa kana kuti kunyandura maari rudo kutozosvikira irwo rwada . ’
Kuita kuti shamwari dzako dzizive paumire nenzira yakafanana kungaderedza imwe yedzvinyiriro yadzo .
Chinoisvokosha kupfuura zvose , musikana wechiShuramiti akanga akashinga kudzivisa kutamburira kuri kose kwakaita mambo kumuita kuti achinje pfungwa .
“ Ini ndiri rusvingo , ” akazivisa kudaro nomutoo wokudadirira .
Unofanira kuzviratidza umene kuva akashinga kudaro kana toreva nezvezvisina kufanira .
Kufanana nomuShuramiti , unofanira kudzidza kuva akanaka pakuramba .
Kana kuita kudaro kwakakuomera , rovedza kuramba mumigariro isina kunyanyokomba .
Rovedza kuomerera pane chaunodavira .
Ipapo kana migariro yakaoma ikasvika , uchava akagadzirira zviri nani zvikuru kubata nayo .
Dzivisa Kupfimba Ikoko
Zvino ngatirangarirei dzimwe nyengedzo dzakarovedzeka dzinoshandiswa navakomana namarangaririre aunofanira kudziita :
‘ Munhu ari wose anokuita . ’
Usakudavire !
Nzvero yakaitwa nesangano rinonzi Planned Parenthood yakazivisa kuti 53 muzana yavasikana vane makore 17 muUnited States vakapinda muvatano .
Zvisinei , ikoko kunosiya 47 muzana vasina — kubatanidza newe !
Kunze kwezvo , maKristu haa‘teveri boka ’ kana nheyo dzeBhaibheri dzichiputswa . — Eksodho 23 : 2 .
‘ Uri kuzviita mwana . ’
Handizvo !
Vanhu vakura vanorondedzerwa muBhaibheri sa “ avo kupfurikidza nokushanda vane masimba avo okufunga akarovedzwa kutsauranisa zvose zviri zviviri zvakarurama nezvisina kururama . ” — VaHebheru 5 : 14 , NW .
‘ Une ngava yayo neni . ’
Hauna ngava yevatano nomunhu upi noupi — angave waunofunda naye , mubatirwi , shamwari , kana kuti munhu upi noupiwo zvake !
Uye hakuna munhu ana maruramiro okuiraira .
‘ Oh , tinorarama chinguvana .
Tingafa mangwana ! ’
SamaKristu , tinotarisira mberi kuupenyu husingaperi .
Hatingagoni kubvumira chinguvana chimwe chomufaro wevatano isingabvumirwi kuparadza nguva isingaperi yomufaro . — 1 VaKorinte 15 : 32 - 34 .
Kupfimba kunonyengera kwakadaro kunoda — mhinduro dzakananga — padzimwe nguva dzakajeka .
Uye kana mumwe munhu achipfuurira , ungada kurangarira zvikuru mapindurire auchaita munhuyo nomutoo unobudirira zvikuru .
Chipi kana chipi chaunotaura , ratidza kuti uri kurevesa pamusoro pokuramba zvikarakadziro zvake zvevatano ; usaita nokushamiswa kana kuti nokukwenudzwa .
Munyori Joyce Jillson anokarakadzazve , kuti : “ Kana uchida zvomenemene kunyaradza nhau dzacho kwechigarire , pinda mukurukurirano yorudzidziso . ”
Pwere zhinji dzechiKristu dzakawana ikoku kuva kwechokwadi .
Anodaro mumwe musikana : “ Pari pose apo mumwe munhu anoedza kundipfimba , ndinobudisa Nharireyomurindi . ”
Hungu , imwe yedziviriro dzakanakisisa ndeyokujekesa zvitendero zvako .
Ita kuti munhu wacho azive chikonzero nei uri kuramba zvikarakadziro zvake zvevatano .
Hausiri kumuramba chaizvoizvo somunhu asi uri kuramba chiito chaanoda kuita .
Mutoo wakadaro wokurangarira unobetsera zvikurukuru kana munhu ari mumwe munhu waunofanira kunangana naye zuva nezuva .
Kana achifarira shoko reBhaibheri , mutezo wechirume weungano yechiKristu unogona kudzokerera .
Sezvineiwo , kuna vamwe vasingagoni kurangarirwa navo .
Zvaunogona kuita bedzi ndiko kutsanangura chimiro chako nomutoo wakajeka , usinganyemwereri — ndokuenda hako .
Kana kunetsa kuchipfuurira kana kuti mugariro wacho wakanyanyokuomera zvokusagona kubata nawo , taura nhau dzacho navabereki vako .
Vangava nezvikarakadzo — kana kuti vangasarudza kupindira .
Mune zvimwe zvinoitika , ungatofanira kutiza mugarirowo ! — Enzanisa naGenesi 39 : 12 .
Zvino , ungatambura kutukwa kana kuti kunetswa somuuyo wechimiro chako , asi rega kuora mwoyo .
Kufanana nomuShuramiti , uchafarikanya rugare runoparirwa nokuita chiri chakarurama .
Kunze kwezvo , handi vakomana vose vachaita nomutoo wokutuka .
Mambo Soromoni , kunyange zvazvo akarambwa nomusikana , haana kufunga zvakashata pamusoro pake .
Kutaura idi , akanyora imwe yenziyo dzake dzakaisvonakisisa dzorudo dzati dzamboitwa , achimurumbidza !
Nomutoo wakafanana , vakomana vazhinji vacharemekedza chimiro chako choushingi .
Uye kana vakasadaro ?
Ingopfuurira bedzi kuva akashinga kudaro somuShuramiti .
Iva “ rusvingo ” uye kwete se “ suo ” rinozarurwa zviri nyore .
Yeuka : Garikano yako isingaperi nokuzviremekedza zviri pamutanhiko !
