Unogona sei kubata navakomana vasingagamuchiri aiwa nokuda kwemhinduro ?
Harisati Richingova Bedzi Ravana
Mumwe mukadzi wokuFort Worth , Texas , anonyora , kuti : “ Ndava nebhuku rinonzi KuTerera kunoMudzidzisi muKuru kwechiverengero chakati chamakore .
Ndakasarudza kuvamba kuriravira mwanakomana wangu ane mwedzi gumi .
Zuva rimwe nerimwe ndinorava maganhuro maviri kana kuti matatu .
Ndinoziva kuti achiri muduku zvokusagona kurinzwisisa .
Zvisinei , ini pachangu ndakabetserwa naro zvikuru .
Bhuku racho rakatapura mwoyo wangu nenzira chaiyo zvikuru ndokukudziridza rudo rwangu nokuonga nokuda kwaJehovha Mwari noMwanakomana wake , Jesu Kristu .
Ndine makore 27 okukura .
Ndaifunga kuti bhuku rinonzi Mudzidzisi muKuru rakanga richingova bedzi ravana , uye zvino ndinozvidemba kuti handina kurinzvera pakuvamba . ”
Zadza ndokuposita kuponi iri , uye iri bhuku rine butiro rakasimba , rine mifananidzo ramapeji 192 richatumirwa kwauri .
Ndingada kugamuchira bhuku ramapeji 192 rinonzi KuTerera kunoMudzidzisi muKuru .

Nzira Iyo Vanachiremba Vanogonana Nayo neAIDS
NGOZI yokubatira AIDS kupfurikidza neropa yaparira vamwe vanachiremba vokuvhiya kushandisa icho The New York Times inoidza kuti “ chipfeko chakakwana chitsva chavanachiremba vokuvhiya nokuda kwenhambo yeAIDS . ”
Kuna chiremba wokuvhiya chipfeko chakakwana ichocho chinobatanidza “ magamubhutsu , fasikoti refu zvikuru risingapindi mvura , magirovhosi maviri , zvidziviriro zvamaoko zvisingapindi mvura namagogoro ameso . ”
Uye nokuda kwokuvhiya chaiko kuzere neropa , inodaro Times , “ ngowani ine chidziviriro chinoputira chiso . ”
Nomutoo unokosha , kunenge kukupera kwa 1990 , Nzvimbo Dzokudzorwa Kwehosha dzakataura kuti pazvirwere zveAIDS 153 000 zvakashumwa , 637 vaiva vanachiremba , 42 vaiva vanachiremba vokuvhiya , 156 vanachiremba vamazino nevezvoutsanana , uye vane 1 199 vaiva vakoti .
AIDS yakatanga kuzivikanwa muna 1981 .
Kwenguva yakati kuti yakanga yakaganhurirwa zvikurukuru kuvarume vanovatana navapindwi muropa nemirimo vaitapurwa nenariti dzejekiseni dzakashatswa .
Asi kupararira kwayo pakati pavakadzi kwave kuchikurumidza .
World Health , magazini yeWHO ( World Health Organization ) , rakashuma muchinyorwa charo chaNovember - December 1990 , kuti : “ Chiverengero chavakadzi [ munyika yose ] chinokarirwa kuva chinorwara neAIDS mukati mamakore maviri anotevera chichapfuura hwerengedzo inowedzera yezvirwere zvose zveAIDS zvakashumwa kuWHO mukati memakore gumi okutanga omurakatira wacho . ”
MuUnited States , Nzvimbo dzeMubatanidzwa Dzokudzorwa Kwehosha dzakashuma kuti pakasvika kupera kwa 1990 , kwaiva navanhu vane 15 696 vanopfuura zera ramakore 50 okukura vakanga vava nezviratidzo zveAIDS .
Ichecho chiverengero chikuru pakuenzanisirwa nezvirwere zvine 2 686 bedzi zveAIDS muvana vari pasi pamakore 13 , boka ravanyajambwa veAIDS rakaparidzirwa zvikuru kwazvo .
Ko vakuru vanobatira sei AIDS ?
Vazhinjisa vanodaro somuuyo wevatano yavane mitezo mimweyo yokubereka .
