Mavara Anogarwa Nhaka Anoita Rutivi Rukuru
Ko mavara anogarwa nhaka akakutapura zvakadini ?
Rongedzero yeDNA , yakawanwa mumachromosome anopfuudzira mavara enhaka , ine rondedzero nemirairidzo zvakarongwa nokuda kwokukura kwomunhu mumwe nomumwe .
Naizvozvo hukuru hwakadini hwetsika dzako umene hunopesvedzerwa mumavara anogarwa nhaka ?
Kunooneka sokunge kuti kuchine chinetso mukubvumikisa batano ipi neipi chaiyoiyo pamavara anogarwa nhaka uye hunhu .
Zvisinei , kune mimwe mitoo inoratidzika kuva ine kodzero .
Somuenzaniso , chiverengero chakati chemiitiro yako yokunyama yakagarwa nhaka chine chokuita chapakarepo patsika dzako .
Nokudaro , vanhu vazhinji vane kufungira mano nepfungwa dzinodeya kurangarirwa pamusoro paavo vorumwe ruvara rweganda kana kuti dzinza .
Mukadzi ane pamuviri anogona kubetsera kana kuti kukuvadza mwana wake asati aberekwa kupfurikidza nemiitiro yake amene , mifungo , uye mirangariro .
