Chaizvoizvo mingani yemipimo yako uye zviito zvakatapurwa norudzidziso ?
Nepo rudzidziso ruchifanira kuita sechidziviso patsika dzisingavimbiki , dzoutsotsi , vanhu vazhinji vari kutapurwa nokubatana kwavo norudzidziso nenzira yakasiana .
