Chingakutsamwisa here ?
Ngatimbomirei zvishoma ndokufungidzira nyika yakakwana umo munhu ari wose akachena , ane utano hwakanaka , anofara , uye akatendeseka ; umo kunyange avo vari muchiremera vane mutsa uye vanorangarira , vanofarira kuitira vamwe zvakanaka ; umo musina makaro , uye musina munhu anodyeredzera mubiyake ; umo vana vanoteerera vabereki vavo vane ushamwari , vanotarisira ; umo musina kufufutirwa nehasha — musina masimba masimba , musina utsotsi , musina utere ; umo vanhu vanovimba uye vanofara kupfurikidza nomusikirwo ; umo upenyu hunogona kufarikanywa nepfungwa yechengeteko negarikano .
Unogona kuzviona umene uchikodzera munyika yakadaro here , kudai nyika Yakaisvonakisisa kudaro yaizombovapo ?
