Nzira Yaunogona Kuchinja Nayo Zvauri
CHII chave chichishaikwa mumitoo yebumbiro retsika nechinjo zvatokurukurwa ?
Zvinoshuviwa zvomunhu amene neshandiswo yesimba rokuzvisarudzira !
Kushandiswa kwechido chesimba rake amene rokuzvisarudzira kupfurikidza nechisarudzo chokuchenjera chomunhu oga .
Mukupfupikisa , kuzvidzora kwake kuri kushaikwa !
Vezvokurapa vane tsika vakawana kuti vane bviro iri nani zvikuru yokuwana nayo miuyo inogara narini kana munhuyo ari kurapwa ane chiremera chokuita chisarudzo chokupedzisira mukugadza nharidzano dzake amene dzetsika .
Vance Parkard akanyora mubhuku rake rinonzi The People Shapers , kuti : “ Sezvinooneka kupfurikidza nezano duku , munhu upi noupi ane mufungo anoziva anogona zvino kuva muderedzi wetsika dzake amene . ”
Ikoku kunonzi kuzvitarisira .
Namamwe mashoko , uko mwero wakati wokuzvidzora unoshandiswa , vandudziko dzakatanhamara dzakacherekedzwa .
MaKristu ane betsero apo kuzvidzora kunodikanwa , nokuti akadzidza kushandisa ikoku sechimwe chezvibereko zvipfumbamwe zvomudzimu mutsvene waMwari .
Ikoku kunoreva kuti simba rinobata basa raMwari Wamasimba ose rinogona kuitwa kuti rive nechokuita pakuchinja kwetsika dzako ndokukubetsera kuti ubudirire .
Naizvozvo , chii chaunoda kuita pamusoro petsika dzako ?
Unoda kuchinja zvomenemene here ?
Kana zvakadaro , kubva pachii ?
Kuchinjira kuchii ?
Uye neiko ?
Unogona kuvimba nokuzvidzora kwako umene here ?
Ndokupi kwaunogona kuwana yamuro inogovera betsero bedzi ?
Ngatinzverei mimwe yemitoo uye mativi zvokuchinja nazvo mitoo yetsika .
Nhano 1 : Wana Zvauri Zvomenemene
Iwe uri mumbishi nokuda kweicho unoda kuva .
Hunhu hutsva hwako hunofanira kuvakwa kupfurikidza nokuchinja hunhu hwako hwekare .
Naizvozvo unofanira kuzviziva umene nomutoo wakarurama .
Unogona here kurondedzera kuti mativi api etsika dzako aungada kuchinja ?
Zvakwakaoma kuziva tsika dzako umene , unodikanirwa kunzvera mupimo unoremekedzwa nounovimbika .
Bhaibheri Dzvene rinorumbidzwa nokuda kwaikoku .
Shandisa Bhaibheri , uye uchawana murangariro wako umene waungave usina kuona kare .
Ungatove usati uchida zvaunoona zvichiratidzirwa , asi unogona kuva nechokwadi chokuti uchava mufananidzo wakarurama .
Bhaibheri rakafananidzirwa nechionioni , uye vanhu vanokurudzirwa kunzvera mariri .
“ Kana munhu upi noupi ari munzwi weshoko , uye asati ari muiti , iyeyu akafanana nomunhu anotarira chiso chake chomuzvarirwo muchionioni . Nokuti iye anozviona amene , uye anoenda hake uye pakarepo anokanganwa kuti iye munhu worudzii .
Asi uyo anonzvera mutemo wakakwana uri worusununguko uye anopfuurira mauri , uyu munhu , nokuti akava , kwete munzwi anokanganwa , asi muiti webasa , achava anofara mukuuita kwake . ”
Bhaibheri , richinzwisiswa uye richishandiswa nomutoo wakakodzera , rine simba guru , rinokamuranisa mukupedza nharo risati richizongoratidzira bedzi zvauri somunhu asi kunyange kuzivisa vavariro dzako uye zvimiro zvendangariro .
Nokudaro , Pauro akanyora , kuti : “ Shoko raMwari ibenyu uye rinoshandisa simba uye rinopinza kupfuura munondo upi noupi unocheka kuviri . . . uye rinogona kucherekedza mifungo nevavariro dzomwoyo . ”
Shoko raMwari rinotopfuura kupfurikidza nokugovera nhungamiro pamusoro pechiri chakarurama zvechokwadi nechiri chisina kururama zvechokwadi . — VaHebheru 4 : 12 ; 5 : 14 , NW .
Bhaibheri rinogona kukuitira zvinhu zvose izvozvi nemhaka yokuti iro iShoko raJehovha , Mwari wechokwadi ane mano okucherekedza .
Mukuwirirana nePisarema 139 , Mwari anokunzvera wose ndokuita kamuraniso yakarurama yezvauri .
Pis 139 Ndima 1 ( NW ) , inoti : “ Haiwa Jehovha , imi makandinzvera , uye imi munondiziva . ”
Mwari ave achikutarisira chifo chokunambwa .
Anosanokuziva chose chose .
Iye akaita kuti tsinhiro dzoupenyu hwomunhu dzinyorwe muBhaibheri mumibatanidzwa yose inobvira .
Uchazviwana umene uchiratidzirwa pane imwe nzvimbo mumapeji aro , nomutoo wakanaka kana kuti zvimwe nomutoo wakaipa .
Nokudaro , unogona kuwana zvauri zvomenemene — kana uchida kudaro .
Nhano 2 : Sarudza Zvaunoda Kuva
Kana uchizochinja , iva nechokwadi chokuti chinjo ichava yakakukodzera .
Iva nechokwadi chokuti ndizvo zvaunoda uye kuti zviri nani kupinda zvauri zvino .
Inharidzanoi dzetsika dzakavandudzwa dzaunofanira kugadza ?
Ndokupi kwaunogona kuwana pangiro yakarurama pamiitiro yetsika dzinodikanwa ?
Zvakare , Bhaibheri rinorumbidzwa nokuda kwaikoku .
Bhaibheri rinokukurudzira kuchinja nokuda kwezviri nani zvikuru , kuchinjira ku “ hunhu hutsva . ”
Pauro akapa zano , rokuti : “ Imi munofanira kubvisa hunhu hwekare hunowirirana nenzira yomufambiro wenyu wekare uye huri kushatiswa mukuwirirana noruchiva rwahwo rwunonyengedza ; asi . . . munofanira kuitwa vatsva musimba rinovandudza ndangariro yenyu , uye munofanira kupfeka hunhu hutsva uhwo hwakasikwa mukuwirirana nokuda kwaMwari mukururama kwechokwadi noruvimbiko . ”
Bhaibheri rinokuratidza iyo iri iyi miitiro iri nani zvikuru .
Unoyeuka nyika yakakwana yarondedzerwa kare here ?
Kana iwe uchida kuva rutivi rwenyika iyeyo , uchatofanira kuona dikanwo yokuvandudza mavara anorondedzerwa pana VaKorose 3 : 12 - 17 , mavara akadai sokunzwira urombo , mutsa , kuzvininipisa , unyoro , shiviriro , kanganwiro , rudo , rugare , uye kuonga .
Naizvozvo pashure pokunzvera Bhaibheri rako , gadza nharidzano dzako .
Dzinyore .
Ipa nharidzano imwe neimwe nzvimbo yokutanga .
Ishandire !
Nhano 3 : Tsvaka Mienzaniso Yakafanira
Zhinji dzetsika dzako dzakaumbwa nokuzvifananidzira kwako navamwe — shamwari , vasonganiri , vabereki , vadzidzisi vokuchikoro .
Kuregererei , ipapoka , pashure pokusarudza nharidzano dzako dzetsika dzinoshuviwa , kutsvaka mumwe munhu anozvibata zvakanaka nenzira yaunoshuva kutevedzera ?
Ipapo tsvaka betsero yomunhu iyeyo .
Nomutoo wokuchenjera chirevo cheBhaibheri chinoratidzira , kuti : “ Iye unofamba navanhu vakachenjera achava akachenjera . ” — Zvirevo 13 : 20 , NW .
Bhaibheri rine nhauro youpenyu hwomuenzaniso wakanakisisa nokuda kwedu tose , Jesu Kristu amene .
Rava nezvokuti akazvibata sei mumigariro yose , mufambiro wake wetsika , mano ake okufunga nouchenjeri , chiremera chake , kuva nomufungo kwake nomutsa wechienzi uye kuitira hanya munhu biyake .
Anozorodza sei mashoko ake apo iye anoti : “ Uyai kwandiri , imi mose munotambudzika nokuremedzwa , uye ini ndichakuzorodzai .
Isai joko rangu pamuri uye dzidzai kwandiri , nokuti ini ndiri munyoro nounozvininipisa mumwoyo , uye muchawana zororo nokuda kwemweya yenyu .
Nokuti joko rangu rine mutsa uye mutoro wangu wakareruka ” ! — Mateo 11 : 28 - 30 , NW .
Mamirioni ari munyika dzose akatotendeukira kuna Kristu Jesu somuenzaniso wawo uye anoita napaanogona napo kutevedzera tsoka dzake , kungofanana naiyewo , akafamba munzira yakarairidzwa naBaba vake vokudenga , Jehovha Mwari .
Aya mamirioni , agutsikana netsika dzavo dzakashata dzenyika yose zvayo nhasi , akatendeukira kuungano yomunzvimbomo yeZvapupu zvaJehovha nokuda kwebetsero nenhungamiro uye havana kuodzwa mwoyo .
PaHoro dzoUmambo dzazvo , mienzaniso yechiito yakaisvonaka yakafanana neyaKristu yakawanda , uye betsero yakawanda yakagoverwa kuna avo vanoda kuchinja tsika dzavo dzomunhu oga kuchimwe chinhu chiri nani zvikuru .
Chokwadika , Zvapupu zvine utera hunozivikanwa norudzi rwomunhu rusina kukwana ; bva izvo zvinewo simba romudzimu rakanaka rinovandudza ndangariro . — VaEfeso 4 : 23 .
Nhano 4 : Kuwana Simba Raunoda Kuti Ubudirire
Kuchava kunonyaradza kuna avo vanoda kuchinja nzira dzavo kuziva kuti betsero inowanika .
“ Hunhu hutsva ” hunorondedzerwa se “ hwakasikwa mukuwirirana nokuda kwaMwari mukururama kwechokwadi nokuvimbika . ”
Ikoku kunosimbisira kuti betsero inopfuura yohunhu inowanika kuna Mwari amene nokuda kwaavo vanoida .
Unogona sei kuwana betsero yaJehovha Mwari ?
Imwe yebetsero dzinoisvokosha ndiwo munyengetero womunhu oga .
Munyengetero unogovera basa rekurukurirano inokosha naManyuko esimba riri madikanwa kuchinja nzira dzako .
Munyengetero unokubvumira kutaura norusununguko uye wakafaranuka panguva ipi neipi , kunyange pakati penjodzi .
Kusvika kwakadaro kuna Mwari chaiye naanoitira hanya kunopfuura zvikuru kusvika kubetsero ipi neipi yohunhu uye kunoshanda pakarepo .
Nokudaro , muapostora Johane aigona kunyora , kuti : “ Ichi ndicho chivimbo chatinacho kwaari , kuti , pasinei hapo nechiri chatinokumbira mukuwirirana nokuda kwake , iye anotinzwa . ”
Uye mashoko omuporofita Isaya anotikurudzira , kuti : “ Tsvakai Jehovha , imi vanhu , apo achiri angawanika .
Danai kwaari apo achiri anobvumikisa kuva ari pedyo . Wakaipa ngaasiye nzira yake , uye munhu anokuvadza mifungo yake ; uye ngaadzokere kuna Jehovha , uyo achamunzwira ngoni , uye kuna Mwari wedu , nokuti iye achakanganwira nenzira huru . ” — Isaya 55 : 6 , 7 , NW .
Fundo yeBhaibheri inogoverawo simba , ichikugovera zorodzo , ichikugonesa zuva nezuva kurereudzirazve ngwariro panharidzano dzako .
Bhaibheri rinogovera simbaradzo yakanaka sezvaunosvasvavirira chipfuro chako chakasarudzwa chetsika .
Kupfuurirazve , rinokuchidzira pfungwa yokusema nzira dzako dzekare .
Zuva nezuva uchipinza zivo yeBhaibheri uye zviri mukati zvaro zvichabatirawo kutsvikinyidzira kunze mashoko api naapi anopiwa asina kururama angapinda achibva kumanyuko enyika uye mugadziriro dzayo dzedzidzo .
Misangano yechiKristu inogoverwa paHoro yoUmambo yomunzvimbomo yeZvapupu zvaJehovha haingogoveri bedzi dzidzo pamusoro pemipimo yeBhaibheri asi inoitawo kuti tsigiro yeboka uye kuchidzirano kutsika dzakavandudzwa zviwanike .
Iyi tsigiro inogoverwa kupfurikidza neungano yabetsera vazhinji kuita chinjo yetsika inobudirira .
Kuregererei kukurukura betsero yakadaro nomunhu wawakagamuchira kwaari iyi magazini ?
Nhano 5 : Gonana Nokutadzazve
Vazhinji vakaedza kuvandudza nzira dzavo asi vakaodzwa mwoyo nokutadzazve kungave kusingadzivisiki .
Muuyo wacho wakava wokuti vamwe vanorega zvachose .
Vakadarovo vanowanzofunga kuti kana icho vakarangarira setariro yavo bedzi zvino chakundikana , hakuchitongorina tariro .
Ipapo nenzira yokuti chinoitika chakadeya kutemwa , vanozvipa kupesvedzero dzenyika .
Kazhinji kazhinji vanova vakaipisisa kupfuura vasati vaedza kuchinja .
Ramba uchiva nechokwadi iwe umene chokuti nzira ipi neipi yekare isingashuviwi yakafanirwa nokuisiya .
Muapostora Pauro akanongedzera kutsika dzake dzekare namararamire somurwi wamarara , kana kuti zvinhu zvisina maturo .
Naizvozvo kana iwe , mukuita chinjo , uchigumburwa nemhinganidzo kana kuti kutadzazve , simukazve , uye ramba uchienderera mberi .
Pfuurira !
Ramba uchirwa !
Kuchava kwakakukodzera !
Yeuka , zhinji dzenzira dzako nemiitiro zvakaiswa pauri namasimba okunze anopfuura chisarudzo chako kana kuti udzori panguva iyeyo .
Masimba iwawa achiri kushanda .
Uchaarega achikumbandidzira muforoma yawo here ?
Aiwa ?
Ipapoka usatongorega !
Mamirioni avanhu vanobva mutsika dzakasiana - siana — kunyange matsotsi navanhu vaibatanidzwa zvikuru mumufambiro woutere — vakachinja murubudiriro tsika dzavo .
Vakachengeta mipimo yavo yakavandudzwa kusvikira kuzuva rino , vazhinji kwamakumi amakore , vachinamatira kunzira dzavo dziri nani neperero inoshuviwa yokuzvidira .
Asi vanoonga Mwari nokuda kwesimba nesundo yokukuita .
Sokutaura kwakaita muapostora Pauro : “ Ndine simba rokuita zvinhu zvose kupfurikidza naiye anopa simba kwandiri . ” — VaFiripi 4 : 13 , NW .
Vari kukunda mukurwa kwokuita chiri chakarurama .
Iwewo unogona kuchinja kana uchida zvomenemene , uye iwe unogona kufarikanya upenyu munyika itsva yaMwari . — Pisarema 37 : 29 ; 2 Petro 3 : 13 .
