Avo vanochinja vanogonawo kugara nhaka pasi rakachinjwa
Vechiduku Vanobvunza Kuti . . .
Misangano yechiKristu Inogona Sei Kundibetsera ?
“ Ini handifungi kuti machechi anokubetsera kuenderera mberi mumudzimu .
Ndinoreva kuti , mutoro womunhu wacho kana iye achida kuva womudzimu kana kuti kwete . ” — Kevin wezera ramakore 19 .
KEVIN akarurama mumativi mazhinji .
Zvomenemene mutoro womunhu mumwe nomumwe kusarudza “ kana iye achida kuva womudzimu kana kuti kwete . ”
Asi zvauri kurava iyi nyaya , kunopfuura zvingabvira kuti zvimwe unoda kuva womudzimu .
Kunyange zvakadaro , ungave usina chokwadi chaichoicho chokuti chii chaizvoizvo chiri munhu womudzimu kana kuti unogona kuva sei mumwe .
Mumutauro wakapfava , munhu womudzimu ndouyo anoisa mirangariro yake , mifungo , uye zviito pasi penhungamiro inoitwa naMwari Wokumusorosoro , Jehovha .
Anorangarira Musiki wake pakuita zvisarudzo zvezuva nezuva , achigadza nharidzano , kana kuti kugadza zvinhu zvokutanga muupenyu .
Namamwe mashoko , munhu womudzimu munhu ane ndangariro yakarerekera kuna Mwari .
Sowechiduku , ungawana kuti “ funganyo dzetsika ino yezvinhu ” inopinganidza kukura kwako kwomudzimu .
Kuva anofanira kusonganirana muswere wose wezuva navadzidzi biyako vangave vaka‘kombamira kukuita zvakashata nguva yose ’ kunogonawo kuva kunoodza mwoyo .
Vamwe vangato “ tuka uye kutaura pamusoro pezviri zvakashata , ” vachikuomesera kurereudzira ndangariro yako pazviri zvakanaka .
Uye kana vabereki vako kana kuti mimwe mitezo yemhuri vasingagoverani newe kutenda kwako , vangagovera rukurudziro ruduku , kana ruchitongovapo , rwomudzimu .
Unogona kuitei kukurira idzi pesvedzero dzakashata ndokukura mumudzimu ?
Chimwe chinhu chaunogona kuita ndechokupinda misangano paHoro yoUmambo yeZvapupu zvaJehovha nguva dzose .
Mukusafanana neminamato yechechi , misangano ikoko inokukurudzira zvose zviri zviviri kuronda “ kuzvipira kwoumwari sevavariro yako ” uye kukubetsera muenderero mberi yako kubva muuhwana hwomudzimu kuukuru hwomudzimu . — 1 Timotio 4 : 7 ; VaEfeso 4 : 13 , 14 .
Misangano Inokubetsera Kudzidza
Muungano dzinopfuura 63 000 mupasi rose , Zvapupu zvaJehovha zvinotevera pangiro yeBhaibheri yokuti “ unganidza vanhu , varume navakadzi navana vaduku . . . kuti vagoteerera uye kuti vagodzidza . ”
Naizvozvo uchawana vechiduku vakawanda vakafanana newe vari pakati peZvapupu .
Zvapupu zvaJehovha munyika yose zvinogoverana purogiramu imwe cheteyo yedzidzo .
Iyoyi inoumbwa nemisangano mishanu yevhiki nevhiki , mumwe nomumwe unotora rinenge awa muurefu .
Misangano mishanu yacho ndeiyi :
Musangano Wavose — hurukuro yeBhaibheri inosimbisa musoro weBhaibheri .
Fundo yeNharireyomurindi — fundo yakadzama yedzidziso dzeBhaibheri uchishandisa magazini yeNharireyomurindi , chinyorwa chikuru cheZvapupu zvaJehovha .
Chikoro Choushumiri Choubati Ushe hwaMwari — chinodzidzisa unyanzvi hwokutaura nokuda kwoushumiri hwechiKristu .
Musangano Webasa — unopa kurukurirano nemienzanisiro yemitoo yedzidziso dzinobudirira nokuda kwoushumiri hwapasuo nesuo uye fundo yeBhaibheri .
Fundo yeBhuku yeUngano — kurukurirano yemibvunzo nemhinduro inoitwa mumapoka maduku kuchishandiswa yamuro yeBhaibheri — kazhinji kazhinji mudzimba dziri dzoga .
Mapurogiramu edzidzo pamisangano iyi anogona kukubetsera kudzidza “ kunyange zvinhu zvakadzama zvaMwari . ”
Zvisinei , kune dzimwe betsero dzinobva mukupinda .
“ Sesimbi Inorodza Simbi ”
“ Kuri nyore kuva muKristu kana uri pana vamwe vanobatirawo Mwari , ” anodaro Michelle wezera ramakore 15 .
“ Asi apo unoenda kuchikoro , kwakaoma zvikuru nokuti vadzidzi biyako vane chirongwa chakasiana chemipimo nenharidzano . ”
Naizvozvo , imwe betsero yokupinda misangano , ndiro banza rokusonganirana navatendi biyako .
Mambo akachenjera Soromoni akati : “ Sesimbi inorodza simbi , naizvozvo munhu anorodza mano omumwe . ”
Padzimwe nguva , “ mano ” edu omudzimu , ndiko kuti , zivo yedu yomudzimu nenzwisiso , zvinodikanirwa kuva zvinorodzwa .
Asika sezvo kurodza banga chairoiro kuchida unyanzvi uye midziyo yakarurama , naizvozvo unodikanirwa kusonganirana navanhu vakarurama , avo vane mano o “ kupa chipo chomudzimu kwauri . ” — VaRoma 1 : 11 , NW .
PaHoro yoUmambo , uchawana vanhu vakadaro , vamazera akasiana , madzinza , namarudzi .
Nomutoo unonzwisisika , ungakweverwa kuvezera rako .
Kunyange zvakadaro , ipa ngwariro chaiyo kuna avo vakapedza makore akawanda vachibatira Jehovha mukutendeka .
Ruzivo rwavo rwokuzviwanira muupenyu pamwe chete nezivo yavo huru yeBhaibheri zvinogona kukubetsera zvikuru .
Unogona sei kuziva vakadaro ?
Edza kuvabvunza mibvunzo , yakadai sokuti , ‘ Makapinda sei muzvokwadi ? ’
kana kuti , ‘ Basa romumunda rakanga rakadini pamaiveri muduku ? ’
Vangasanobudisa zvipo zvomudzimu nokuda kwako !
Chokwadi , pakusvika vamwe vari muungano , pakutanga unganzwa sezvakaita Craig wezera ramakore 12 , uyo akati : “ Ndaisitya kutaura navanhu vakura .
Ndaifunga kuti kana ndikataura chinhu chisina kururama , ndingapiwa zano . ”
Craig zvino anoziva kuti kunzwa kwake kwakanga kusina kudzama .
“ Ndinotaura navo zvino ndakasununguka , ” iye anotsanangura kudaro .
Kuregererei kuita nhamburiko imwe cheteyo yokusonganirana navanhu vakakura mumudzimu muungano ?
